;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"25 Best Tools for Freelancers to Scale a Real Business\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-tools-for-freelancers/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-tools-for-freelancers/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 18 Dec 2018 10:31:11 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"free and premium plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"freelancer plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"freelancer tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=225113\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:618:\"<p>Are you looking for the best tools for freelancers? No matter what kind of freelancing you do, the right tools can help you increase your productivity, stay organized, and secure clients with ease. In this article, we’ll share our handpicked list of the 25 best tools for freelancers. Get your clicking finger reading because you’re [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-tools-for-freelancers/\">25 Best Tools for Freelancers to Scale a Real Business</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31916:\"<p>Are you looking for the best tools for freelancers? No matter what kind of freelancing you do, the right tools can help you increase your productivity, stay organized, and secure clients with ease.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll share our handpicked list of the 25 best tools for freelancers. Get your clicking finger reading because you’re going to want to visit these links!</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">1. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/wpforms.png\" alt=\"WPForms\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224560\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/wpforms.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/wpforms-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/wpforms-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Every freelance website needs a killer contact form in order to succeed. Fortunately for you, WPForms is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)\">best contact form plugin for WordPress</a> available on the market.</p>\n<p>However, WPForms is capable of so much more than an average contact form plugin. It can also be used as a booking form to make appointments with potential clients.</p>\n<p>Or, with the signature addon, you can use it to securely get client signatures on contracts, terms of services agreements, or services documents.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with WPForms Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/timedoctor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Time Doctor</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/timedoctor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Time-Doctor.jpg\" alt=\"Time Doctor\" width=\"748\" height=\"270\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225179\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Time-Doctor.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Time-Doctor-300x108.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Tracking your time helps increase your productivity. When you’re “on the clock,” even as a freelancer, you’ll free that gentle pressure to finish quickly and efficiently. Time Doctor is simple to use, and will keep you from giving into your urges to procrastinate.</p>\n<p>Better still, Time Doctor can be used to log your hours for clients. If you’re working for hourly rates, this tool is a must-have in order to make sure you’re paid what you earned.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/timedoctor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Time Doctor Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/startbooking/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. StartBooking</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/startbooking/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/StartBooking-1.png\" alt=\"StartBooking\" width=\"775\" height=\"241\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225180\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/StartBooking-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/StartBooking-1-300x93.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/StartBooking-1-768x239.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>StartBooking is a plugin for WordPress websites designed so business owners and freelancers can effortlessly schedule appointments with clients.</p>\n<p>As a freelancer, you can use this plugin to create and track your meetings with potential clients and steady clients. It allows you to personalize your client schedule sheets so you can get the full potential out of every meet-up.</p>\n<p>Organize your schedule, save relevant meeting information, and so much more; all from the comfort of your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/startbooking/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with StartBooking Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. BirchPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/birchpress.jpg\" alt=\"birchpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225181\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/birchpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/birchpress-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/birchpress-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If StartBooking isn’t your cup of tea, then you may prefer BirchPress as your online booking tool. BirchPress puts booking in the hands of your clients, allowing them to schedule your services online via its handy-dandy forms.</p>\n<p>With BirchPress, you can create booking forms, schedule appointments with clients, and even accept online payments. It has an intuitive form building interface that’s very beginner-friendly.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with BirchPress Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads-custom-deliverables/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Easy Digital Downloads Custom Deliverables</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads-custom-deliverables/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/EDD-Custom-Deliverables.jpg\" alt=\"customdeliverablesdesign\" width=\"748\" height=\"298\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225182\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/EDD-Custom-Deliverables.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/EDD-Custom-Deliverables-300x120.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Easy Digital Downloads Customs Deliverables is the perfect freelancer tool if you want an easy way to deliver files and receive payments. The smooth interface allows you to create an account and link multiple clients to your account. </p>\n<p>As you complete your work, you can add the files to your client&#8217;s account and they can download and view them with 1 click. Easy Digital Downloads Customs Deliverables is an incredibly easy way for you stay organized and deliver your work files with a quick click of your mouse. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads-custom-deliverables/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Easy Digital Downloads Custom Deliverables Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://trello.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Trello</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://trello.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Trello.jpg\" alt=\"Trello\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225183\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Trello.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Trello-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Trello-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>It doesn’t matter if you’re a freelancer who works in a group, or a lone wolf, you can benefit from Trello. The goal of this online program and fully-featured application is to make organizing your tasks for the day, week, month, and even year a breeze! </p>\n<p>Trello has a number of features including the ability to make task cards. Simply put, you organize your tasks for the day, whether it be writing assignments, image creation, or HTML work, and as you complete the tasks you can check them off. The sense of organization will give you some serious peace of mind and make your work day a piece of cake. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://trello.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Trello Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://pomodoneapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. PomoDoneApp</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://pomodoneapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/PomoDoneApp.jpg\" alt=\"PomoDoneApp\" width=\"748\" height=\"279\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225184\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/PomoDoneApp.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/PomoDoneApp-300x112.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Are you a freelancer who already works with programs like Asana, Evernote, and Trello? If so, PomoDoneApp is a fantastic way to bring all of your work together from those platforms in 1 easy-to-use application. </p>\n<p>As you finish your work assignments from clients, you can use your free PomoDoneApp account to create files and upload them directly to your client&#8217;s account. Once your client logs in, they can click on your uploaded work files and access them instantly.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://pomodoneapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with PomoDoneApp Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.skype.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Skype</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skype.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Skype.jpg\" alt=\"Skype\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225185\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Skype.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Skype-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Skype-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We all know communication is important, especially if you’re a freelancer. Skype is a common, but necessary, free tool that you should download now if you haven&#8217;t already. </p>\n<p>When using Skype, you can communicate with clients through text-based instant messages. But there&#8217;s more to it than that! This application allows you to have voice calls, including groups calls, so that you can easily collaborate and get your questions answered and your workflow going in the right direction.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skype.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Skype Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://asana.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Asana</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://asana.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Asana.png\" alt=\"Asana\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225186\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Asana.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Asana-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Asana-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Not freelancing on your own? If you have an entire team to manage, then Asana is the perfect project management tool.</p>\n<p>Asana organizes your team’s tasks and conversations in one easy-access area, keeping you from wasting time with multiple emails. Thanks to taking email inboxes out of the picture, Asana keeps teams on track, boosts efficiency, increases productivity, and bolsters better communication.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://asana.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Asana Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://zoom.us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Zoom</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://zoom.us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zoom.jpg\" alt=\"Zoom\" width=\"748\" height=\"168\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225187\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zoom.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zoom-300x67.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Zoom is a communication tool for freelancers who prefer to voice chat with their clients. You can create a free account and start setting up your client list right away. </p>\n<p>When it comes time to make a phone call, Zoom offers a host of features such as text chat in videos for link sharing, you can video chat using your default webcam, and you can even record your calls in case you need to review them at a later time. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zoom.us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Zoom Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Dropbox</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Dropbox.jpg\" alt=\"Dropbox\" width=\"748\" height=\"232\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225188\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Dropbox.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Dropbox-300x93.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Dropbox is an easy-to-use organization tool for freelancers who have multiple clients. You can create individual folders and give other users (your clients) access to specific folders.</p>\n<p>As you complete your writing, image, or video assignment you can upload it to Dropbox for review. Both client and freelancer can work within the folder at the same time. If you’re looking for a tool to help collaborate with clients and save you time, look no further than Dropbox. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Dropbox Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://slack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Slack</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://slack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Slack.jpg\" alt=\"Slack\" width=\"748\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225189\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Slack.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Slack-300x120.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Slack is a communication tool all freelancers should use when working with a wide range of clients, or even with a small team of clients within the same business. </p>\n<p>You can communicate directly with individuals, make conversations private, create group chats, and instantly search your previous conversations with a search bar at the top of the screen. Slack has revolutionized the way we communicate!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://slack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Slack Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://basecamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. Basecamp</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://basecamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/basecamp.jpg\" alt=\"basecamp\" width=\"748\" height=\"144\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225190\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/basecamp.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/basecamp-300x58.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Basecamp is a slick, easy-to-use platform that allows for seamless communication for freelancers and clients.  When you make a free account, you’ll be able to create folders where you can list your tasks.</p>\n<p>Once you get your clients on board, you can assign them to the tasks and you guys can work together within the folder to lay out current work, view future work, and return to previous jobs to make sure they&#8217;re done correctly. Basecamp is the perfect tool for those seeking a simple-yet-powerful project management platform.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://basecamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Basecamp Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://gsuite.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. G Suite</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://gsuite.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/G-Suite.jpg\" alt=\"G Suite\" width=\"775\" height=\"262\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225191\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/G-Suite.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/G-Suite-300x101.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/G-Suite-768x260.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>G Suite is an all-in-one tool for busy freelancers. There&#8217;re multiple platforms within G Suite (also known as Google Apps) to help keep you organized and productive. </p>\n<p>When you open up G Suite, you’ll see a slew of features like a calendar, access to Google Docs, a Cloud-based sharing system, and more! You can go in and edit the calendar, make appointments, create documents, and easily share them with your clients when you’re finished. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://gsuite.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with G Suite Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://evernote.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Evernote</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://evernote.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Evernote.jpg\" alt=\"Evernote\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225192\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Evernote.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Evernote-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Evernote-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As a freelancer, one of the biggest problems you&#8217;ll likely face is remembering every little thing you need to do on your schedule. You may have a pocket notebook, and that’s great; however, wouldn’t it be better to have unlimited space and access to it any time? If that sounds appealing, you need Evernote. </p>\n<p>Evernote is an accessible application you can use on your smartphone, laptop, or tablet. Quickly jot down notes, appointments, ideas, and future plans; then access them again whenever you need to in seconds.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://evernote.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Evernote Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.lastpass.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. LastPass</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.lastpass.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/LastPass.jpg\" alt=\"LastPass\" width=\"748\" height=\"220\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225193\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/LastPass.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/LastPass-300x88.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Tired of remembering 20+ passwords for all of the sites you frequent daily? If so, LastPass is exactly what you need. This program has a free and premium version that helps you come up with passwords for all of the websites you visit. </p>\n<p>But LastPass takes it a step further by recording and encrypting your passwords so you’ll never have to remember them again. Plus, you’ll never have to worry about falling victim to a hacker. All-in-all, it’s a must-have tool for everyone. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.lastpass.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with LastPass Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/freshbooks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. FreshBooks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/freshbooks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/FreshBooks.jpg\" alt=\"FreshBooks\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225194\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/FreshBooks.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/FreshBooks-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/FreshBooks-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>FreshBooks is an accounting software designed for freelancers and business owners who want to easily manage their funds. There&#8217;s a ton of options available in both the free and premium versions of the application. </p>\n<p>You can easily create and send invoices for quick payments. It’s a breeze to manage your money as their system is clean, user-friendly, and offers features that every budding freelancer needs to grow with. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/freshbooks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with FreshBooks Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Constant Contact</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/constant-contact.png\" alt=\"constant contact\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225195\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/constant-contact.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/constant-contact-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/constant-contact-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re looking to create and send highly-effective emails to your subscribers, Constant Contact is a great choice. As one of the best email marketing services available, it integrates well with the world’s best lead generation plugins, like <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n<p>The customization options are nearly endless, and there are dozens of pre-made templates to get you rolling. Plus, their 24/7 support team is always just a live chat or email away from helping you resolve any issue that may come up.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Constant Contact Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://buffer.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Buffer</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://buffer.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Buffer.jpg\" alt=\"Buffer\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225196\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Buffer.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Buffer-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Buffer-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As a freelancer, there&#8217;s a good chance you have multiple social media accounts that you use to advertise your business and meet new clients. However, sometimes it can be a drag updating your social media accounts multiple times a day. Buffer makes social media easy. </p>\n<p>You can program multiple accounts and schedule posts for the future. Many people use the application to make their weekly posts and schedule them for set times. Obviously, you can keep an eye on your account; but, once you schedule your posts for the day, you’re good to go! Set up your social media posts, forget them, and focus on what you do best.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://buffer.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Buffer Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.canva.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. Canva</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.canva.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Canva.png\" alt=\"Canva\" width=\"775\" height=\"288\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225197\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Canva.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Canva-300x111.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Canva-768x285.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Images are great conversion tools. Whether you use them for landing pages or blog posts, visual elements increase your chances of success.<br />\nWith Canva, you can design your own images, infographics, icons, and banners without an expensive piece of editing software. And it’s so easy to use, you can do all of your visuals yourself, without having to hire a professional designer.</p>\n<p>Canva runs in your browser and comes with a ton of free templates to assist you. Once you’ve finished, simply export your creation, save it, and use it on your freelance website.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.canva.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Canva Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://piktochart.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Piktochart</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://piktochart.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/piktochart.jpg\" alt=\"piktochart\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225198\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/piktochart.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/piktochart-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/piktochart-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>When you’re a freelancer, it can be challenging for you to hire a designer, check on progress, make changes, etc. Piktochart is here to make your life easier.</p>\n<p>Piktochart uses an intuitive interface that allows you to make infographics, reports, flyers, posters, and presentations. You’ll be able to go in and create your item of choice with a simple drop and drag system that gives you flexibility and customization options beyond your wildest dreams!  </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://piktochart.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Piktochart Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. LiveChat Inc.</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/LiveChat-Inc.png\" alt=\"LiveChat Inc\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225199\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/LiveChat-Inc.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/LiveChat-Inc-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/LiveChat-Inc-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Never miss another opportunity to answer a potential client’s questions. With LiveChat Inc., you can connect with your website’s visitors instantly and provide them with answers right when they need it most.</p>\n<p>With this real-time chat plugin for your freelancing website, you can sway clients to buying your products or services just by talking to them. The best freelancer is an available freelancer!</p>\n<p>LiveChat Inc. also provides reports on how to place your chat box for optimal engagement, as well as an in-depth analysis of how your visitors are interacting with it.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with LiveChat Inc. Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/editorial-calendar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Editorial Calendar</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/editorial-calendar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Editorial-Calendar.png\" alt=\"Editorial Calendar\" width=\"775\" height=\"236\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225201\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Editorial-Calendar.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Editorial-Calendar-300x91.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Editorial-Calendar-768x234.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Prefer to look at the big picture? If you&#8217;re a freelance blogger (or simply a freelancer with a blog), then Editorial Calendar is a must-have. It allows you to see posts that have already been published, as well as scheduled posts, for the entire month. </p>\n<p>One of our favorite features of this plugin is it allows you to move your posts via a simple drag and drop interface. You can easily set up your schedule for the month, edit posts from within the plugin, and make quick changes as needed.</p>\n<p>Editorial Calendar allows you to schedule posts from multiple authors, making future planning easy as pie. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/editorial-calendar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Editorial Calendar Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/collabpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">24. CollabPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/collabpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/CollabPress.jpg\" alt=\"CollabPress\" width=\"775\" height=\"273\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225204\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/CollabPress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/CollabPress-300x106.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/CollabPress-768x271.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>CollabPress is a developer tool for WordPress users that helps freelancers schedule posts and activities. In other words, you can put your work projects in the background and check off the list as you complete each task. </p>\n<p>This application comes with a calendar, email reminders, and an intuitive activity log. If you’re tired of being disorganized, then Collabpress is a plugin that&#8217;ll make your life easier.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/collabpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with CollabPress Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/q2w3-fixed-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">25. Q2W3 Fixed Widget</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/q2w3-fixed-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Q2W3-Fixed-Widget.jpg\" alt=\"Q2W3 Fixed Widget\" width=\"775\" height=\"230\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225205\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Q2W3-Fixed-Widget.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Q2W3-Fixed-Widget-300x89.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Q2W3-Fixed-Widget-768x228.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The Q2W3 Fixed Widget was designed for freelancers who want to build a website with ease. The main function of this application is to allow you to quickly and easily organize segments within your content. </p>\n<p>You can make easy-to-follow planners and informative pieces by quickly dragging and placing headers, widgets, and content boxes. If you’re a freelancer and having trouble with your website, then the Q2W3 Fixed Widget plugin can help! </p>\n<p>We especially love the option to promote your freelancing services via a sticky widget on your WordPress website.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/q2w3-fixed-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Q2W3 Fixed Widget Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best tools for freelancers.</p>\n<p>If you found this post useful, you might also like our in-depth comparison of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared (2018)\">9 best email marketing services</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-tools-for-freelancers/\">25 Best Tools for Freelancers to Scale a Real Business</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-tools-for-freelancers/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"How to Track Affiliate Links in Google Analytics (Easy Way)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-track-affiliate-links-google-analytics/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-track-affiliate-links-google-analytics/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 17 Dec 2018 12:59:47 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Google Analytics\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"google analytics affiliate tracking\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"monsterinsights tutorial\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=225285\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:625:\"<p>Want to learn how to track affiliate links in Google Analytics? By tracking your affiliate links, you can find out exactly how your users are interacting with them on your site. Then, using the gathered data, you can optimize your links for better conversions and revenue. In this article, we’ll show you how to track [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-track-affiliate-links-google-analytics/\">How to Track Affiliate Links in Google Analytics (Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11862:\"<p>Want to learn how to track affiliate links in Google Analytics? By tracking your affiliate links, you can find out exactly how your users are interacting with them on your site. Then, using the gathered data, you can optimize your links for better conversions and revenue. </p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to track affiliate links in Google Analytics in 3 easy steps. </p>\n<h3>Why Track Affiliate Links?</h3>\n<p>Without a doubt, affiliate marketing is one of the most popular ways to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\">make money online</a>. If you have a good amount of regular traffic coming to your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a>, you can earn a tidy sum of money by adding affiliate links on your site. Affiliate links are links to sales pages for other people’s products with your affiliate id attached. So, when people buy products through that link, you earn a certain amount of commission money. </p>\n<p>When managed properly, affiliate marketing can give you good perennial income. However, successful affiliate marketing isn’t possible without proper data and analytics. You need actual statistics on how your users are interacting with the affiliate links to optimize said links and to run affiliate marketing campaigns well. </p>\n<p>That’s why you need to track your affiliate links. Here’re few benefits of affiliate link tracking: </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Get actual data on user interaction:</strong> You can find out exactly how users interact with your affiliate links. Analyze where people are clicking the most.</li>\n<li><strong>Identify your most profitable links:</strong> Find out which links are leading to the most conversions and focus on them.</li>\n<li><strong>See most converting pages:</strong> View which pages are leading most affiliate sales and optimize them for more revenue.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In a nutshell, affiliate tracking helps you to see how users view and interact with your affiliate links. It provides comprehensive data with which you can optimize your affiliate marketing strategies and maximize your earnings. </p>\n<h3>Tracking Your WordPress Affiliate Links in Google Analytics</h3>\n<p>Google Analytics is the best web analytics platform available on the market. It helps you track your entire website traffic and their interactions on your site. As such, affiliate tracking is just 1 type of metric that Google Analytics tracks. </p>\n<p>Although Google Analytics has the ability to track a wide variety of metrics, advanced tracking like affiliate links and eCommerce reports are a bit tricky for beginners to set up. Fortunately, there’s an EASY way to use Google Analytics in WordPress: <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a>.  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"MonsterInsights\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224562\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights is the most popular WordPress Google Analytics plugin on the web. It simplifies the whole process of using Google Analytics in WordPress. Using MonsterInsights, you can set up Google Analytics affiliate tracking in just 2 minutes. </p>\n<p>But, before that, you’ll need to add and manage your affiliate links properly in WordPress. So, we’ve parted this tutorial in 3 steps as given below: </p>\n<h3>Step 1: Managing Your Affiliate Links in WordPress Using ThirstyAffiliates</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/thirstyaffiliates/\">ThirstyAffiliates</a> is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-for-affiliate-marketers/\">best affiliate management plugin for WordPress</a>. It allows you to add your affiliate links from one place in your dashboard, organize them by categories, and manage them efficiently. Most importantly, it allows you to cloak your affiliate links (i.e. to transform long complex affiliate links into short pretty links). </p>\n<p>For example, here’s what an affiliate link normally looks like: </p>\n<p><strong>https://example.com/products/?product_id=123&#038;affiliate_id</strong></p>\n<p>Now, you can cloak the link and make it short like the branded URL shown below:</p>\n<p><strong>http://www.yoursite.com/recommends/product-name</strong></p>\n<p>The main benefit of managing affiliate links with ThirstyAffiliates is that it stores your affiliate links in your site&#8217;s backend, so you can find the links easily anytime you want to add them to content. They’re searchable by names. </p>\n<p>Second, cloaking transforms long, ugly affiliate links into pretty links. It also makes the affiliate links look like internal links which are actually external. This prevents your users from seeing direct affiliate links and enhances your chances of getting more clicks.</p>\n<p>Best of all, using an affiliate link management plugin allows you to easily track your affiliate links in Google Analytics. MonsterInsights affiliate tracking also uses cloaked links for tracking.</p>\n<p>So, your first task is to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">install ThirstyAffiliates</a> and add your affiliate links to its interface. It’s easy to add and manage your affiliate links using this plugin. </p>\n<p>If you need detailed instructions, check out our tutorial on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-add-affiliate-links-in-wordpress-with-thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\">how to add affiliate links in WordPress with ThirstyAffiliates</a>. </p>\n<p>After you add and manage your affiliate links with ThirstyAffiliates, you’re ready to set up affiliate tracking with MonsterInsights. </p>\n<h3>Step 2. Setting Up Affiliate Tracking in Google Analytics Using MonsterInsights</h3>\n<p>Setting up affiliate tracking with MonsterInsights is really simple. It’ll take just a few clicks to complete the setup process.</p>\n<p>To get started, you’ll need to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">install MonsterInsights</a> on your WordPress site. Then, connect your site with Google Analytics using MonsterInsights. It’s easy to set up Google Analytics with this plugin. </p>\n<p>If you need detailed instructions, here’s our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-google-analytics-wordpress-site/\">how to set up Google Analytics in WordPress with MonsterInsights</a>. </p>\n<p>After the setup process is complete, you’re ready to set up affiliate tracking. </p>\n<p>Navigate to <strong>Insights &raquo; Settings</strong> from your WordPress dashboard and then click on the <strong>Tracking</strong> tab at the top of the page. Then, go to the <strong>Affiliate Links</strong> tab in the left taskbar.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-affiliate-tracking-setup.png\" alt=\"monsterinsights-affiliate-tracking-setup\" width=\"775\" height=\"680\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225308\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-affiliate-tracking-setup.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-affiliate-tracking-setup-300x263.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-affiliate-tracking-setup-768x674.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>There, you’ll see 2 fields:</p>\n<p><strong>1) Set path for internal links to track as outbound links:</strong></p>\n<p>In this field, you’ll need to specify the path for internal links to track as outbound links. When using an affiliate management plugin like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ThirstyAffiliates</a>, your affiliate links will look like an internal link. </p>\n<p>For example, your affiliate may look like this:  <strong>http://yoursite.com/recommends/product-name</strong></p>\n<p>In the above example, the link looks like an internal link however it redirects to an outbound link (i.e. an affiliate link). And, your affiliate links are cloaked with <strong>/recommends/</strong>.  </p>\n<p>Now, you’ll need to paste <strong>/recommends/</strong> in this field, so that Google Analytics can identify which internal links are affiliate links. If you use multiple prefixes, you can separate them with a comma: /recommends/,/out/.</p>\n<p><strong>2) Label for those links:</strong></p>\n<p>The label in your Google Analytics report lets you identify where the click came from. For example, you can add a label <strong>aff</strong> to your affiliate links.</p>\n<p>After you complete these 2 fields, click <strong>Save Changes</strong>.</p>\n<p>That’s it. You’re done with affiliate link tracking setup.</p>\n<h3>Step 3: Viewing Affiliate Link Tracking Reports</h3>\n<p>Now that you’ve set up affiliate tracking in WordPress with MonsterInsights, you may be curious how to view the reports. So, here it is!</p>\n<p>With MonsterInsights, you can view your most important <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/feature/google-analytics-dashboard/\" target=\"_blank\">analytics reports right inside your WordPress dashboard</a>. To view your affiliate reports, go to <strong>Insights &raquo; Reports &raquo; Publishers</strong> from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/affiliate-links-reports-monsterinsights-dashboard-reports.png\" alt=\"affiliate-links-reports-monsterinsights-dashboard-reports\" width=\"775\" height=\"882\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225305\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/affiliate-links-reports-monsterinsights-dashboard-reports.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/affiliate-links-reports-monsterinsights-dashboard-reports-264x300.png 264w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/affiliate-links-reports-monsterinsights-dashboard-reports-768x874.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>This report shows you the 10 best affiliate links for your site. If you want to see more than that, you can click the <strong>View All Affiliate Links Report</strong> button at the bottom of the report. That will redirect you to <strong>Behavior &raquo; Events Top Events</strong> in your Google Analytics account. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/top-events-ga-reports.png\" alt=\"top-events-ga-reports\" width=\"775\" height=\"457\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225310\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/top-events-ga-reports.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/top-events-ga-reports-300x177.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/top-events-ga-reports-768x453.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to learn how to track affiliate links in Google Analytics. </p>\n<p>You may also want to see our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-amazon-affiliate-store-wordpress-make-money/\">how to create an Amazon affiliate store with WordPress</a>. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-track-affiliate-links-google-analytics/\">How to Track Affiliate Links in Google Analytics (Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-track-affiliate-links-google-analytics/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"6 Best Image Optimization Plugins for WordPress (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-image-optimization-plugins-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-image-optimization-plugins-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 14 Dec 2018 10:36:08 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"best image optimization plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"best image optimizer WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"image optimization plugin review\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=224930\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:639:\"<p>Are you looking for the best image optimization plugins for your website? That&#8217;s a good idea! Every great website needs images to grab the attention of visitors. Whether you&#8217;re a blogger, an eCommerce site, or a small business, images make your website look professional. But, if you&#8217;ve got a lot of images on your site, [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-image-optimization-plugins-wordpress/\">6 Best Image Optimization Plugins for WordPress (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13410:\"<p>Are you looking for the best image optimization plugins for your website? That&#8217;s a good idea! Every great website needs images to grab the attention of visitors. Whether you&#8217;re a blogger, an eCommerce site, or a small business, images make your website look professional. But, if you&#8217;ve got a lot of images on your site, you&#8217;ll also need image optimization plugins to make sure your site is running at top speed. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you the best image optimization plugins. </p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-7\">At a Glance: 6 Best Image Optimization Plugins for WordPress</h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-7\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-7\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">Plugin</th><th class=\"column-2\">Price</th><th class=\"column-3\">Active Installs</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shortpixel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ShortPixel Image Optimizer</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">From $9.99 (one-time plan)</td><td class=\"column-3\">100,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/automatic-image-compression/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automatic Image Compression</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">From $29</td><td class=\"column-3\">Not available</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/seo-friendly-images-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">SEO Friendly Images Pro</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">From $20</td><td class=\"column-3\">Not available</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resmushit-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">reSmush.it Image Optimizer</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">40,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ewww-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">EWWW Image Optimizer</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">700,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tiny-compress-images/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Compress JPEG &amp; PNG Images</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">100,000+</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- #tablepress-7 from cache -->\n<h3>Why Do You Need Image Optimization Plugins for Your WordPress Site?</h3>\n<p>Images on your website make your content more engaging for readers. They&#8217;re a must-have on your site if you want your visitors to stick around long enough to become customers. But images are much larger in size than plain text. Because images are so much larger, they can slow your website&#8217;s speed down to a snail&#8217;s pace. </p>\n<p>Having a speedy website is important. Users today have no time or patience to sit around and wait for your website to load. In fact, <a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/page-load-time-conversion-rates\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">47 percent</a> of customers expect a web page to load in 2 seconds or less. So, if your website doesn&#8217;t load fast enough, users will abandon your site in search of someone else&#8217;s. </p>\n<p>But what can you do to speed up your site while keeping your important images? That&#8217;s where image optimization plugins come in. </p>\n<p>To improve the speed of your WordPress site, you need to optimize your images. Image optimization plugins can optimize your images for you automatically, so you don&#8217;t have to know a thing about photo editing or code. And you don&#8217;t have to worry about sacrificing the quality of your images either. </p>\n<p>Not only does optimizing your images help with speeding up your website, it also improves your search engine optimization (SEO) as well. </p>\n<p>All of these image optimization plugins will optimize the photos on your site so that your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress website</a> is speedier and your site gets found more easily by users searching the web.</p>\n<p>Get ready to make your website lightning fast. Check out our list of the best image optimization plugins for WordPress.      </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shortpixel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Shortpixel Image Optimizer</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shortpixel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Shortpixel-830x465-e1542817169180.jpg\" alt=\"shortpixel-image-optimization-plugins\" width=\"740\" height=\"414\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224936\" /></a></p>\n<p>ShortPixel Image Optimizer is an awesome WordPress image optimization plugin. The plugin installs directly into your WordPress dashboard where you can easily manage the image reduction process. As soon as the plugin is installed, every new image you upload to your site will be automatically compressed. You can also use the ShortPixel plugin to compress all of the images previously uploaded to your site with just the touch of a button.</p>\n<p>With this powerful plugin you can compress JPEG, PNG, GIF (still or animated) images, and PDF documents. There&#8217;s no file size limit and you can optimize thumbnails as well as featured images.  </p>\n<p>You can use ShortPixel Image Optimizer for free and optimize up to 300 images per month. If you need to optimize more than 300 images per month, you can upgrade to a bigger plan starting at only $4.99. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shortpixel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with ShortPixel Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/automatic-image-compression/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Automatic Image Compression &#038; Bulk Image Compression</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/automatic-image-compression/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/automatic-image-compression-e1542817534756.png\" alt=\"automatic-image-compression-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"740\" height=\"349\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224942\" /></a></p>\n<p>Automatic Image Compression &#038; Bulk Image Compression for WordPress by wpslash is a great tool to optimize and compress all your images. It&#8217;s lightweight and simple to use so you can quickly improve the performance of your website. </p>\n<p>This plugin will automatically compress JPEG, PNG, and GIF images as you upload them; or you can compress images in bulk all at once. With Automatic Image Compression &#038; Bulk Image Compression there are no limits on file size or number of images you can compress. </p>\n<p>Automatic Image Compression &#038; Bulk Image Compression costs only $29 for a regular license and includes future updates and 6 months of support from wpslash. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/automatic-image-compression/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Automatic Image Compression &#038; Bulk Image Compression Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/seo-friendly-images-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. SEO Friendly Images Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/seo-friendly-images-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SEO-friendly-e1542817918366.png\" alt=\"seo-friendly-images-pro-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"740\" height=\"357\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224943\" /></a></p>\n<p>SEO Friendly Images Pro for WordPress by Pascal-Bajorat is another useful image optimization plugin for your WordPress site. This plugin doesn&#8217;t compress your images but it&#8217;s a full-featured solution for SEO friendly images. </p>\n<p>SEO Friendly Images for WordPress automatically optimizes all alt and title attributes of images in your posts, pages, and third party plugins. Alt and title attributes are important to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\">improve your website ranking</a> in search engine results. This powerful plugin can also optimize your links by automatically adding title attributes based on its content. Another cool feature is their Lazy Loader which boosts your website&#8217;s speed and performance by delaying the loading of images in long web pages that the user won&#8217;t see until they keep scrolling. </p>\n<p>A regular license for SEO Friendly Images Pro is only $20 and, with that, you get future updates and 6 months of support to help you if you run into any problems.  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/seo-friendly-images-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with SEO Friendly Images Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resmushit-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. reSmush.it Image Optimizer</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resmushit-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/resmush-it-e1542818200670.png\" alt=\"resmush-it-image-optimizer-plugins\" width=\"740\" height=\"240\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224945\" /></a></p>\n<p>reSmush.it Image Optimizer is quickly becoming one of the most popular image optimization plugins available. This plugin allows you to optimize your images as you upload and they also offer a bulk operation to optimize all of your previously added images in just 2 clicks. </p>\n<p>The reSmush.it plugin accepts JPEG, PNG, GIF, BMP, and TIF files but only up to 5mb. You also have the option to exclude certain photos from being optimized in case you need to add an image to your site in full size. </p>\n<p>A huge plus is that reSmush.it is totally free to download and use. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/resmushit-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with reSmush.it Image Optimizer Today!</a> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ewww-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. EWW Image Optimizer</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ewww-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/EWWW-image-e1542818579456.jpg\" alt=\"ewww-image-optimizer-wordpress-plugins\" width=\"740\" height=\"240\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224946\" /></a></p>\n<p>EWWW Image Optimizer is another powerful image optimization plugin for your WordPress website. With this awesome plugin you can automatically optimize new images as you upload them as well as the images you&#8217;ve already uploaded to your site. </p>\n<p>This plugin gives you the option to convert your images to the best file format. You can also choose the pixel perfect compression or high compression options. That way your image quality looks exactly the same to users. </p>\n<p>EWWW Image Optimizer boasts no speed limits and unlimited file sizes. They also provide free image backups to store your original photos for 30 days. </p>\n<p>Their plugin is free to download but if you want additional features, you can upgrade with one of their API plans. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ewww-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with EWWW Image Optimizer Today!</a> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tiny-compress-images/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Compress JPEG &#038; PNG Images</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tiny-compress-images/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tinypng-e1542818908548.jpg\" alt=\"tiny-png-image-optimization-plugins\" width=\"740\" height=\"240\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224947\" /></a></p>\n<p>Compress JPEG &#038; PNG Images by TinyPNG is another great WordPress plugin to compress your images and make your website faster. You can automatically optimize new images on upload and easily optimize images in bulk that are already on your site. </p>\n<p>You can set a maximum width and/or height so that you can automatically resize large image uploads. There&#8217;s no file size limits and you can preserve copyright metadata, creation date, and GPS location in your original images if you need to. </p>\n<p>Compress JPEG &#038; PNG Images is free to download and use but only for 100 images per month. If you need to optimize more images each month you can upgrade your account. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tiny-compress-images/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Compress JPEG &#038; PNG Images Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope you enjoyed this article on the best image optimization plugins. Now you&#8217;re ready to optimize your images and make your site speedier. Not only will you be happier with a super fast site, but your website visitors and customers will be happier too. </p>\n<p>If you were a fan of this article, check out our post on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\">7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared</a>. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-image-optimization-plugins-wordpress/\">6 Best Image Optimization Plugins for WordPress (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-image-optimization-plugins-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"43 Simple WordPress Themes to Easily Start a Website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://www.isitwp.com/simple-wordpress-themes-easily-start-website/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://www.isitwp.com/simple-wordpress-themes-easily-start-website/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 13 Dec 2018 10:44:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"simple themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"simple wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"start a website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=224114\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:622:\"<p>Do you want a simple WordPress theme for your WordPress website? A theme is a template that includes features for the design and look of your site. Many beginners search for simple themes that aren&#8217;t bloated with extra features so they can quickly set up and launch their website without asking help from expensive web [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/simple-wordpress-themes-easily-start-website/\">43 Simple WordPress Themes to Easily Start a Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54234:\"<p>Do you want a simple WordPress theme for your WordPress website? A theme is a template that includes features for the design and look of your site. Many beginners search for simple themes that aren&#8217;t bloated with extra features so they can quickly set up and launch their website without asking help from expensive web developers; however, with so many themes available, finding the right one can prove frustrating.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s why, in this article, we&#8217;ll share our handpicked list of the 43 best simple WordPress themes so you can choose one and start your website in no time flat.</p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-3\">Quick Info: Top 5 Simple WordPress Themes</h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-3\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-3\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">Theme</th><th class=\"column-2\">Price</th><th class=\"column-3\">Uniqueness</th><th class=\"column-4\">Released by</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-workstation-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Workstation Portfolio Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Workstation Pro</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$99.95</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best for Displaying Hero Images</td><td class=\"column-4\">StudioPress</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-corner/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Corner\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Corner</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">from $35 / year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best Minimalist Theme</td><td class=\"column-4\">CSS Igniter</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-shape/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shape\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Shape</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$58 / year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best Portfolio Theme</td><td class=\"column-4\">Tesla Themes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Ambiance Pro</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$99.95</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best Full-width/ No Sidebar Theme</td><td class=\"column-4\">StudioPress</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-enterprise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Enterprise\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Enterprise</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$58 / year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best Corporate Theme with Built-in Forums</td><td class=\"column-4\">Tesla Themes</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- #tablepress-3 from cache -->\n<h3>Creating a Website with a Simple WordPress Theme</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-website-builders-for-beginners-compared-2018/\" title=\"10 Best Website Builders for Beginners Compared (2018)\">popular website builder</a> in the world. Many of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">biggest brands are using WordPress actively</a> on their websites.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find 2 kinds of WordPress websites. First, there&#8217;s WordPress.com, which is a hosted solution. Then, there&#8217;s WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted platform.</p>\n<p>To create a simple website, you&#8217;ll need to select self-hosted WordPress.org. But, before you start, you&#8217;ll also need to buy a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a>.</p>\n<p>We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>. It&#8217;s a well-renowned web hosting company, and is also officially recommended by WordPress.org.</p>\n<p>Luckily, they&#8217;re offering our users a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on the web hosting.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog on bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> has agreed to provide you, as an IsItWP reader, a web hosting plan with 60% off on the regular hosting price. You can start your website for just $2.75 per month. </p>\n<p>After purchasing the web hosting, you can follow our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to make a website</a>.</p>\n<p>Ready? Next, scroll through our handpicked list of simple WordPress themes choose the best one for your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-workstation-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Workstation Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Workstation Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-workstation-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Workstation Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/workstation.jpg\" alt=\"Workstation Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224140\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/workstation.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/workstation-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/workstation-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Workstation Pro is a simple WordPress theme for your personal and professional websites. It&#8217;s built on the well-known Genesis framework which gives the theme a solid foundation. It has an easy-to-use options panel and you can also customize the theme settings with the live preview. The homepage and other pages are widget-based, so you can easily drag and drop features to develop your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-corner/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Corner\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Corner</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-corner/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Corner\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/corner.jpg\" alt=\"Corner\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224141\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/corner.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/corner-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/corner-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Corner is a beautiful WordPress theme with all the useful features you need for your website. It&#8217;s not bloated with features like the big themes and has a simple design. It comes with a widget-based layout to easily drag and drop widgets on the homepage and other pages. Corner has multiple color schemes, and a lot of custom settings for WordPress websites.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-shape/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shape\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Shape</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-shape/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shape\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shape.jpg\" alt=\"Shape\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224142\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shape.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shape-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shape-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Shape is a modern WordPress theme for the fitness, health, photography, images, and other websites. It supports a grid-based layout to showcase your photos. It works great with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared (2018)\">best image gallery plugins</a> to create filterable galleries in WordPress. Shape has homepage sections like portfolio, services, clients, team, and more. It comes with custom widgets, color options, multiple layouts, and Google Maps integration.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Ambiance Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ambiancepro.jpg\" alt=\"Ambiance Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224143\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ambiancepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ambiancepro-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ambiancepro-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ambiance Pro is a stylish WordPress theme with widget ready layout. You can easily drag and drop widgets to the homepage with multiple widget areas. This theme is built on the popular Genesis framework. It has unlimited color choices, page templates, gallery post formats, and more. Ambiance Pro is easy to set up and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">optimized for SEO</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-enterprise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Enterprise\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Enterprise</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-enterprise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Enterprise\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Enterprise.jpg\" alt=\"Enterprise\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224134\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Enterprise.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Enterprise-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Enterprise-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Enterprise is a WordPress theme for business and professional websites. It has a simple and neat design with multiple sections on the homepage to create a beautiful website. It comes with pricing tables, FAQs section, portfolio section, services section, and a homepage <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"11 Best WordPress Slider Plugins for 2018 (Compared)\">image slider</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/maxwell/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Maxwell\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Maxwell</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/maxwell/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Maxwell\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/maxwell.jpg\" alt=\"Maxwell\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224135\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/maxwell.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/maxwell-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/maxwell-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Maxwell is a simple WordPress theme designed specifically for news and magazine blogs. It enables you to display your featured posts with images on the homepage. It comes with 2 navigation menus, featured images, a content slider, crisp typography, and support for post excerpts.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/writee/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Writee\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Writee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/writee/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Writee\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/writee.jpg\" alt=\"Writee\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224136\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/writee.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/writee-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/writee-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Writee is a simple and free theme for personal WordPress websites and blogs. It has features to support writers and bloggers. Writee works great with all the third-party <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"27 Best WordPress Plugins that You MUST Use (2018)\">WordPress plugins that you must have</a> on your blog. It has an image slider that integrates with your posts to show the featured content on your homepage.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Presence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/presence.jpg\" alt=\"Presence\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224137\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/presence.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/presence-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/presence-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Presence is a WordPress theme for business websites. It&#8217;s easy to use and offers ready-made demo websites to quickly launch your business site. It has a simple design that can be used to create any professional website like hotel, restaurant, music, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)\">real estate</a>, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-roxima/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Roxima\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Roxima</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-roxima/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Roxima\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/roxima.jpg\" alt=\"Roxima\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224138\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/roxima.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/roxima-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/roxima-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Roxima is a simple WordPress theme designed specifically for portfolio, business, and personal websites. It has a neat design with a fullscreen image on the homepage. Roxima has multiple layouts, content modules, and sections. It even has a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared (2018)\">drag and drop page builder</a> that you can use to set up your website easily.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-pocket/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pocket\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Pocket</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-pocket/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pocket\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pocket.jpg\" alt=\"Pocket\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224139\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pocket.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pocket-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pocket-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Pocket is a beautiful WordPress theme with simple and tidy design. It comes with minimal-yet-powerful features: a simple navigation menu on top, custom logo, featured image, and stunning typography. Pocket is easy to set up and you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Start a Blog in 2018 – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">start your blog on WordPress</a> in no time.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-atmosphere-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Atmosphere Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Atmosphere Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-atmosphere-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Atmosphere Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/atmospherepro.jpg\" alt=\"Atmosphere Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224145\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/atmospherepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/atmospherepro-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/atmospherepro-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a simple and professional business theme, then select Atmosphere Pro. It&#8217;s also suitable for your portfolio website or personal blog. This theme is based on the Genesis framework and fully supports widget-based layouts. It has multiple templates and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert (2018)\">landing pages</a>. Atmosphere Pro features a 2-column layout, and you can use the live theme customizer to edit your theme settings.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/libretto/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Libretto\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Libretto</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/libretto/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Libretto\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/libretto.jpg\" alt=\"Libretto\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224146\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/libretto.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/libretto-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/libretto-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Libretto is a classic WordPress theme designed specifically for personal blogs. It has an attractive background color, crisp typography, beautiful layout, and more. This theme is optimized for speed and performance. It can also be used to create professional photography and art websites.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-elegant/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Elegant\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. Elegant</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-elegant/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Elegant\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elegant.jpg\" alt=\"Elegant\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224147\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elegant.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elegant-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elegant-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Elegant is a simple WordPress theme for your blog, portfolio, or services website. It supports a custom logo with a navigation menu and social sharing icons. You can select from their multiple layout choices to add your content beautifully. It comes with custom widgets, unlimited color options, ready-made sections, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-paperbag/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Paperbag\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. Paperbag</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-paperbag/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Paperbag\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/paperbag.jpg\" alt=\"Paperbag\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224148\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/paperbag.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/paperbag-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/paperbag-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for simple-yet-modern, stylish WordPress theme with unique typography, then Paperbag is the perfect choice. It has multiple color choices, typography layouts, and custom styling for a WordPress blog. This theme has built-in widgets to quickly add features and content on your website. It features <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins (2018)\">social media sharing icons</a>, a search bar, and a dropdown navigation menu in the header. Paperbag is easy to use and has a lot of custom settings in the theme options panel.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojo-marketplace-daisy/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Daisy\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Daisy</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojo-marketplace-daisy/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Daisy\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/daisy.jpg\" alt=\"Daisy\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224153\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/daisy.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/daisy-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/daisy-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a stylish WordPress theme for your travel website or blog, then Daisy is the theme for you. It has a unique layout with an image slider and services section on the homepage. It fully supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a>, and you can display video thumbnails on your pages.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/karen/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Karen\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Karen</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/karen/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Karen\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/karen.jpg\" alt=\"Karen\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224149\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/karen.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/karen-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/karen-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Karen is a simple blog theme designed specifically for personal WordPress blogs. It features a custom logo with the tagline below it. There&#8217;s a fine space in the header which enables you to add a sentence in the tagline. It also includes social media icons in the header, a search bar in the navigation menu, image slider, multi-column layout, and featured posts section on the homepage.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-igloo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Igloo\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Igloo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-igloo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Igloo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/igloo.jpg\" alt=\"Igloo\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224150\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/igloo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/igloo-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/igloo-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want to create your own restaurant website and need a quick start, then Igloo is the right choice for you. It&#8217;s a WordPress restaurant theme with all the features you need for your eatery. It has a menu management system that can help in displaying your restaurant&#8217;s menu beautifully. It comes with multiple homepage sections like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-testimonial-plugins/\" title=\"10 Best WordPress Testimonial Plugins to Add Social Proof\">testimonials</a>, image gallery, menu, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/baskerville/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Baskerville\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Baskerville</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/baskerville/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Baskerville\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/baskerville.jpg\" alt=\"Baskerville\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224151\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/baskerville.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/baskerville-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/baskerville-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Baskerville is a free WordPress blog theme with simple and clean design for personal and professional blogs. It has a masonry layout which makes it unique from other simple themes. You can pin the featured posts and display them beautifully on the homepage. It comes with a fullscreen header image alongside a navigation menu and search bar. You can easily change the color of the theme to match your brand.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/sanse/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sanse\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Sanse</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/sanse/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sanse\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/sanse.jpg\" alt=\"Sanse\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224152\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/sanse.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/sanse-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/sanse-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sanse is a free and simple WordPress theme. It displays your posts on the homepage without featured images so the page loads faster than usual. The header includes a logo, tagline, and navigation menu. It&#8217;s a no-sidebar theme and supports widgets in the footer area. You can also add a navigation menu in the footer of your website with the Sanse theme.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/barletta/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Barletta\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. Barletta</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/barletta/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Barletta\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/barletta.jpg\" alt=\"Barletta\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224154\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/barletta.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/barletta-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/barletta-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a magazine theme to add lots of content on your website, then Barletta is a great choice. It has an image slider that you can use to display the featured content of your blog. You can create a powerful navigation menu to add on top of the page below the logo. It has color options and custom widgets to create large content websites easily.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-baseline/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Baseline\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Baseline</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-baseline/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Baseline\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/baseline.jpg\" alt=\"Baseline\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224161\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/baseline.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/baseline-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/baseline-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Baseline is a premium WordPress theme designed specifically for health and fitness websites. It has a simple layout with crisp typography that attracts users. It features a content slider, built-in layouts, an infinite scrolling option, and more. It allows you to create a beautiful navigation menu. You can also use Baseline for your magazine or news websites.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-daily-dish-pro-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Daily Dish Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. Daily Dish Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-daily-dish-pro-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Daily Dish Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dailydishpro.jpg\" alt=\"The Daily Dish\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224162\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dailydishpro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dailydishpro-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dailydishpro-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a powerful WordPress blog theme for your personal or professional blog, then Daily Dish Pro is what you need. It comes with custom widgets like About Me that you can add in the sidebar to display your personal biography. It fully supports WooCommerce, and offers several page layouts to customize your blog.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-beatrix/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Beatrix\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Beatrix</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-beatrix/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Beatrix\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Beatrix.jpg\" alt=\"Beatrix\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224163\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Beatrix.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Beatrix-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Beatrix-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Beatrix is a simple WordPress arts and crafts theme. It can be used to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store in 2018 – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">start an online store with WooCommerce</a> for your creative products. It has a beautiful layout with a product slider, social media icons, user login buttons, and more. You can also display your products on the homepage.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">24. Hestia Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/hestia.jpg\" alt=\"Hestia\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224164\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/hestia.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/hestia-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/hestia-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hestia Pro is a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-multi-purpose-themes/\" title=\"24 Best WordPress Multi-Purpose Themes (2018)\">multi-purpose theme</a> for your WordPress website. It recommends a set of free plugins to add features on your website like services, clients testimonials, and more. It has unlimited color choices and font styling options. It&#8217;s responsive and optimized for the search engines.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-medium/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Medium\" rel=\"nofollow\">25. Medium</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-medium/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Medium\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/medium.jpg\" alt=\"Medium\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224165\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/medium.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/medium-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/medium-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Medium is a WordPress blog theme with a multi-column layout on the homepage and other <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert (2018)\">landing pages</a>. It enables you to add a featured image, create sidebar menu, display social links, and show categories menu including post archives. You can easily change the colors, add custom widgets, and use Google Fonts to make a gorgeous website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-camellia/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Camellia\" rel=\"nofollow\">26. Camellia</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-camellia/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Camellia\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/camellia.jpg\" alt=\"Camellia\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224158\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/camellia.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/camellia-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/camellia-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Camellia is a WordPress fashion and lifestyle theme. It has the features you need to create a beautiful personal website. It has amazing color schemes and font options. It also comes with custom widgets, page templates, and more. You can use the live WordPress theme customizer to change its settings and see the preview on the right side of your screen.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-candid/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Candid\" rel=\"nofollow\">27. Candid</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-candid/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Candid\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/candid.jpg\" alt=\"Candid\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224156\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/candid.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/candid-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/candid-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Want a simple storytelling theme for your blog? Candid is a multi-purpose theme for WordPress websites that need a story-based design. It&#8217;s perfect for the photographers, writers, artists, and more. It uses Arbil Display font which makes it unique and stunning for your users. You&#8217;ll also find other theme settings like masonry layout, multi-column choice, unlimited colors, custom widgets, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-truenorth/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TrueNorth\" rel=\"nofollow\">28. True North</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-truenorth/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TrueNorth\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/truenorth.jpg\" alt=\"TrueNorth\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224157\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/truenorth.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/truenorth-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/truenorth-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>True North is a WordPress portfolio theme with a simple and neat layout. It supports a built-in portfolio section on the homepage with other useful sections like a welcome message and a full-width featured image. It allows you to change the background image, header color, social settings, and more using the simple theme options panel. It supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)\">WordPress contact form plugins</a> to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/add-contact-form-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Create a Contact Form on WordPress (the Easy Way)\">add a contact form on your website</a> and engage your users.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-stella/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Stella\" rel=\"nofollow\">29. Stella</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-stella/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Stella\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/stella.jpg\" alt=\"Stella\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224160\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/stella.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/stella-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/stella-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Stella is a modern and stylish WordPress blog theme with a beautiful layout for professional websites. It comes with a stunning content slider, custom header, homepage sections, multiple page layouts, sidebar templates, and more. It&#8217;s easy to set up and most of the theme settings can be managed from the WordPress live customizer.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-suarez/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Suarez\" rel=\"nofollow\">30. Suarez</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-suarez/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Suarez\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Suarez.jpg\" alt=\"Suarez\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224159\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Suarez.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Suarez-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Suarez-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Suarez is a stylish WordPress theme for personal and professional blogs. It has a fullscreen background image on the homepage with logo and navigation menu on top of it. Suarez can be used to create a powerful content website easily. It supports custom content widgets, page templates, animations, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"11 Best WordPress Slider Plugins for 2018 (Compared)\">image slider</a>, and more. The theme is compatible with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/must-have-wordpress-plugins-for-business-websites/\" title=\"25 Must Have WordPress Plugins for Business Websites (Expert Pick)\">best WordPress business plugins</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-montblanc/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mont Blanc\" rel=\"nofollow\">31. Mont Blanc</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-montblanc/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mont Blanc\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/montblanc.jpg\" alt=\"Mont Blanc\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224169\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/montblanc.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/montblanc-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/montblanc-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Mont Blanc is a stunning WordPress theme with multi-purpose features to create any website you need. It comes with a fullscreen background image slider. You can add the logo, navigation menu, text, and other items on top of the slider. It has built-in layouts, homepage sections, image galleries, and more. The settings can be customized from the theme options panel which is quite easy to use.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-basic/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Basic\" rel=\"nofollow\">32. Basic</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-basic/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Basic\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/basic.jpg\" alt=\"Basic\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224177\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/basic.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/basic-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/basic-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Basic is a simple and free WordPress theme with premium-like features. It comes with a lightbox image gallery, social icons, custom widgets, color choices, and more. It supports video thumbnails, footer menu, page layouts, and a scroll to top button. It&#8217;s easy to set up and start your website quickly.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-brittany/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Brittany\" rel=\"nofollow\">33. Brittany</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-brittany/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Brittany\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/brittany.jpg\" alt=\"Brittany\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224170\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/brittany.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/brittany-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/brittany-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Brittany is a colorful WordPress theme for personal blogs. It has a stunning design with unlimited color choices. You can add a navigation menu, social media icons, search bar, and more in the header section. Instead of an image slider on the homepage, there&#8217;s a welcome area for the visitors where you can add your text. Below that, you can display your featured content beautifully. It has multiple page layouts, templates, and custom widgets to personalize your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-primrose/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Primrose\" rel=\"nofollow\">34. Primrose</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-primrose/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Primrose\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/primrose.jpg\" alt=\"Primrose\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224172\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/primrose.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/primrose-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/primrose-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Primrose is a stylish and professional WordPress theme with simple theme options. It has 2 navigation menus, social media integration, featured content slider, and more in the top header. It comes with custom widgets, a variety of color schemes, multiple sidebars, background settings, and more. You can use the live theme customizer with preview to make changes in the theme settings.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cpothemes-allegiant/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Allegiant\" rel=\"nofollow\">35. Allegiant</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cpothemes-allegiant/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Allegiant\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/allegiant.jpg\" alt=\"Allegiant\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224171\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/allegiant.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/allegiant-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/allegiant-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a beautiful and multi-purpose WordPress theme, then select Allegiant. It&#8217;s a simple theme with modern design and powerful features. The theme is suitable for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/\" title=\"How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps (2018)\">small business websites</a>, online magazines, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared (2018)\">eCommerce</a> stores. It features Google Fonts support, custom widgets, color options, and page layouts. It integrates with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a> out of the box to create an online store.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-bluebird/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluebird\" rel=\"nofollow\">36. Bluebird</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-bluebird/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluebird\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluebird.jpg\" alt=\"Bluebird\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224174\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluebird.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluebird-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluebird-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Bluebird is a beautiful WordPress blog theme. It has stunning typography and 2 color choices. Bluebird has multi-sidebars, 2 navigation menus, custom widgets, social links, a content slider, and other useful theme options that&#8217;re easy to use to quickly launch your website or blog.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hueman/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hueman\" rel=\"nofollow\">37. Hueman</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hueman/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hueman\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/hueman.jpg\" alt=\"Hueman\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224173\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/hueman.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/hueman-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/hueman-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hueman is a free WordPress blog theme designed specifically for news and magazine websites. It can be used to create large content sites easily. This theme supports left and right sidebars, a featured content slider, custom widgets, and social media integrations. It comes with a custom logo and navigation menu in the top header. You can also add the navigation menu in the sidebar of your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/flat/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Flat\" rel=\"nofollow\">38. Flat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/flat/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Flat\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/flat.jpg\" alt=\"Flat\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224175\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/flat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/flat-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/flat-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Flat is a free WordPress theme with a flat design for news and magazine websites. It features a left sidebar to add custom logo, navigation menu, search bar, recent posts, and more. The theme design is very simple and neat. It has color options, custom fonts, background color, featured image, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/tracks/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tracks\" rel=\"nofollow\">39. Tracks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/tracks/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tracks\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tracks.jpg\" alt=\"Tracks\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224176\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tracks.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tracks-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/tracks-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Tracks is a stylish and free WordPress blog theme. It can be adapted to create photography, magazine, and personal blogs. It has a minimalist layout with custom logo, navigation menu, social icons, search bar, and more. You can display featured content slider and gallery on the homepage with images. It fully supports video content and works great with all the most popular WordPress plugins.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-landing/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Landing\" rel=\"nofollow\">40. Landing</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-landing/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Landing\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/landing.jpg\" alt=\"Landing\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224178\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/landing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/landing-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/landing-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Landing is a beautiful WordPress theme with support for the custom landing pages and pre-built layouts to quickly launch your website. It has a fullscreen background image with logo, text, call-to-action button, and navigation menu on top of it. You can also change the header layout, colors, fonts, and more. It comes with custom post types like portfolio and event. Landing fully supports WooCommerce, and it&#8217;s <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">multilingual with WPML</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nimble/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nimble\" rel=\"nofollow\">41. Nimble</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nimble/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nimble\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/nimble.jpg\" alt=\"Nimble\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224179\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/nimble.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/nimble-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/nimble-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Nimble is an elegant WordPress blog theme. It has page templates, shortcodes, and other custom options that help in creating a feature rich website easily. It has multiple theme skins, unique color choices, beautiful typography, and more. Nimble is beginner-friendly, and it fully supports<a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-woocommerce-themes-online-store/\" title=\"50+ Best WooCommerce Themes for Your Online Store (2018)\"> WooCommerce</a> to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store in 2018 – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">start an online store</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Float\" rel=\"nofollow\">42. Float</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Float\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float.jpg\" alt=\"Float\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224167\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Float is a premium WordPress theme with simple and parallax design. It has parallax scrolling effects which makes it unique from other themes. The top bar has logo and navigation menu which can be customized from the layout options. Float has multiple built-in layouts that you can use to change the design of your website. It comes with several navigation menu layouts, transparent header options, demo website templates, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-lifestyle-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lifestyle Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">43. Lifestyle Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-lifestyle-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lifestyle Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/lifestylepro.jpg\" alt=\"Lifestyle Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224168\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/lifestylepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/lifestylepro-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/lifestylepro-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Lifestyle Pro is a simple WordPress Genesis theme with powerful features to create a health, fitness, lifestyle, or personal websites. It features 2 navigation menus, custom logo with tagline, sidebar, featured content section, and social media integration. It comes with custom widgets, color options, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a>, and Google Fonts support.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find simple WordPress themes to easily start your website. You may also want to see our handpicked list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-photography-themes-for-wordpress/\" title=\"43 Best Photography Themes for WordPress (2018)\">43 best photography themes for WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/simple-wordpress-themes-easily-start-website/\">43 Simple WordPress Themes to Easily Start a Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://www.isitwp.com/simple-wordpress-themes-easily-start-website/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"24 Best WordPress Themes for Membership Sites (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-membership-sites/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-membership-sites/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 12 Dec 2018 10:46:45 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"best wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"membership themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"premium themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=225279\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:636:\"<p>Looking for the best WordPress themes for membership sites? You’ve come to the right place. We know that, with the perfect theme, your membership site can maximize its earning potential. With the right set of features, you can increase memberships, up engagement, and create a business you can be proud of. That’s why we’ve handpicked [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-membership-sites/\">24 Best WordPress Themes for Membership Sites (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34844:\"<p>Looking for the best WordPress themes for membership sites? You’ve come to the right place. We know that, with the perfect theme, your membership site can maximize its earning potential. With the right set of features, you can increase memberships, up engagement, and create a business you can be proud of.</p>\n<p>That’s why we’ve handpicked the 26 best WordPress themes for membership sites. Each one is fully responsive, so it’ll look great on any device. </p>\n<p>Want a sneak peek? Check out our top 5 favorites in the table below!</p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-9\">At a Glance: Top WordPress Themes for Membership Sites</h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-9\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-9\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">Theme</th><th class=\"column-2\">Price</th><th class=\"column-3\">Unique Because...</th><th class=\"column-4\">Released By</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\" https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"nofollow\">Divi</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$89/year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Shipped with a drag &amp; drop builder</td><td class=\"column-4\">Elegant Themes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ultra</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$49</td><td class=\"column-3\">Bundled with numerous demo sites</td><td class=\"column-4\">Themify</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-public-opinion/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Public Opinion\" rel=\"nofollow\">Public Opinion</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$49</td><td class=\"column-3\">Best for Membership + Magazine Design</td><td class=\"column-4\">CSSIgniter</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-shoppe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shoppe\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shoppe</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$49</td><td class=\"column-3\">Perfect for WooCommerce websites</td><td class=\"column-4\">Themify</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Float\" rel=\"nofollow\">Float</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$49</td><td class=\"column-3\">Supports parallax scrolling</td><td class=\"column-4\">Themify</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- #tablepress-9 from cache -->\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi.jpg\" alt=\"divi\" width=\"748\" height=\"305\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225639\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/divi-300x122.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The first theme we’re going to look at is a jack-of-all-trades theme called Divi. This intuitive theme is perfect for WordPress veterans and newbies alike with its collection of premade theme layouts as well as the ability to build your own theme using their tools from the ground up. </p>\n<p>Divi comes with a host of mix-and-match features, allowing you to freely dip into their 46 different elements, pick what you like, and customize them to fit your site and your brand. </p>\n<p>The fast loading times and instant updates as you tweak and edit your website make this theme an excellent choice for those who want to try something brand new and give their membership site a custom feel in a short amount of time. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Divi Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Themify Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Ultra.png\" alt=\"Ultra\" width=\"775\" height=\"272\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225640\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Ultra.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Ultra-300x105.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Ultra-768x270.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Are you looking for a large collection of professional, handcrafted themes? If so, Themify Ultra is right up your alley! This <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/\">premium responsive theme</a> comes with a whopping 60 custom demos for you to choose from that will instantly spruce up your site.</p>\n<p>The excitement doesn&#8217;t end there! After you’ve picked a preselected layout you can go in and make it your own. There’s nothing like being able to add your own touch to an already brilliant theme, and Themify Ultra allows you that freedom. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Ultra Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-public-opinion/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Public Opinion</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-public-opinion/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/public-opinion.jpg\" alt=\"public opinion\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225641\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/public-opinion.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/public-opinion-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/public-opinion-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Public Opinion, as the name implies, is a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-free-wordpress-blog-themes/\">WordPress magazine theme</a> set designed for webmasters who have newspaper/magazine-themed web pages. The customization options are vast, giving you the chance to build your magazine brand from scratch. </p>\n<p>You can choose from 30 different color options, use an array of layouts that match the style your readers enjoy, and it also gives you just the right amount of space to include advertisements for additional revenue and promotions. </p>\n<p>Once you’ve finished your layout, you can add unique widgets based on the core design of your site. Finally, you’ll get the option to add your own modules so it’s truly a custom creation. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-public-opinion/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Public Opinion Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-shoppe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Themify Shoppe</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-shoppe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shoppe.png\" alt=\"shoppe\" width=\"775\" height=\"380\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225642\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shoppe.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shoppe-300x147.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shoppe-768x377.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Setting up your first eCommerce website doesn’t have to take a specialist when you have this amazing membership theme at your fingertips. They proudly boast that Themify Shoppe allows you to build your website shop and theme in mere minutes.</p>\n<p>You can use Themify Shoppe to tailor your customer’s experience and keep them coming back for more. It’s a breeze to add things like a wish list, quick-look features, and even an Ajax cart for speedy checkouts. </p>\n<p>Combine those amazing tools with the ability to tweak and build upon existing layouts, and it’s no wonder why Themify Shoppe made it onto our list of the best WordPress themes for membership sites! </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-shoppe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Shoppe Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Themify Float</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float.png\" alt=\"float\" width=\"775\" height=\"267\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225643\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float-300x103.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/float-768x265.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Themify Float is what some would call the “futuristic” version of the Themify’s membership themes. The centerpiece is the ability to use parallax images throughout the design templates. </p>\n<p>When you combine the flexible platform options with the varied header, footer, and panel options, you’re left with all the tools you need for a stylish, custom theme. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Float Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-spencer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Spencer</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-spencer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/spencer.jpg\" alt=\"spencer\" width=\"748\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225644\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/spencer.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/spencer-300x154.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Spencer is a membership grade theme for WordPress that’ll help you build an attractive, easy-to-use website while featuring powerful messages. You can customize your theme to match mobile and desktop screens seamlessly with an intuitive drag and drop interface. </p>\n<p>It’s a breeze to create a customized sticky menu that’s always there and ready for your customers to use. Navigation has never been easier. You can also change the color and module locations for a website that perfectly fits your style. </p>\n<p>The most attractive feature of this theme is the ability to deliver your call-to-action in a number of ways. You can use powerful widgets and tools to help boost conversions and turn your bounce rate around. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-spencer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Spencer Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-elegant/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Themify Elegant</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-elegant/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elegant-1.jpg\" alt=\"elegant\" width=\"748\" height=\"276\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225646\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp