pg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/composition-768x134.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The Composition theme from Graph Paper Press was designed from day 1 to make life easier for those who are looking to create a website but don’t really have the required experience. </p>\n<p>Out of the box, this theme comes with a range of tools that you can use to customize your home page, including headers, footers, your home page, and sidebars. Once you have your base layout, you can personalize each page with an easy drop and drag system that allows you to share stories, calendars, photos, and more in seconds. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/graph-paper-press-composition/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Graph Paper Press Composition Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/anariel-design-thinker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. Design Thinker</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/anariel-design-thinker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/thinker.jpg\" alt=\"thinker\" width=\"775\" height=\"335\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225659\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/thinker.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/thinker-300x130.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/thinker-768x332.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Design Thinker is a theme with one core idea behind it: ease of use. You won&#8217;t find any flashy extras that require coding, but it offers a strong framework for new bloggers and entrepreneurs who want to get their foot into the door of the online community. </p>\n<p>You’ll find that Design Thinker includes SEO support right out of the box, so you won&#8217;t have to spend countless hours worried about whether or not you added in those keywords properly. The icing on the cake is the fact that this theme comes with an eCommerce option as well. </p>\n<p>Whether you want to build a traditional blog with just content or an online shop, Design Thinker is an excellent starting premium theme. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/anariel-design-thinker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Design Thinker Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-noozbeat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Noozbeat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-noozbeat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/noozbeat.jpg\" alt=\"noozbeat\" width=\"748\" height=\"254\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225660\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/noozbeat.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/noozbeat-300x102.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Noozbeat is a theme that gives you complete control of your new WordPress website. It starts with the layout. You’ll get full access to a host of easy to use drop and drag tools that allow you to put modules with content exactly where you want them. </p>\n<p>You can then tweak your homepage, header, and sidebars (including adding space for advertisers) to make your site stand out from other blog/magazine style websites on the internet. </p>\n<p>Once you’re done, go through and customize colors and fonts to create your brand, your way. If you want a premium easy to use theme, Noozbeat is a perfect choice. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-noozbeat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Noozbeat Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-indigo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. WPZoom Indigo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-indigo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/indigo.jpg\" alt=\"indigo\" width=\"775\" height=\"470\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225662\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/indigo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/indigo-300x182.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/indigo-768x466.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a website theme that fully supports your goal of having a successful eCommerce site, regardless of your niche, look no further than Indigo. </p>\n<p>You can start selling products almost instantly from your website once you’ve created your own template, or use one of many professional looking templates included out of the box. It’s never been easier to start your own online store, why not start today and see why most businesses are making the transition between brick and mortar and eCommerce. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-indigo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Indigo Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pixelgrade-silk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Pixelgrade Silk</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pixelgrade-silk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/silk.jpg\" alt=\"silk\" width=\"748\" height=\"285\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225663\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/silk.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/silk-300x114.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Do you have a story that you feel like you need to deliver to a greater audience? If so, Pixelgrade Silk is the premium theme you need for a silky-smooth, classy blog. </p>\n<p>The site you build will be optimized for both speed and SEO, meaning you can rest easy knowing that you’re drawing in an audience with your keywords, and they are having a quality experience on your website. Use the simple out of the box tools to create custom pages with expressive stories for the masses. You can even include widgets to make social sharing and newsletter conversions a breeze. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pixelgrade-silk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Silk Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-specialty/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">24. Specialty</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-specialty/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/specialty.jpg\" alt=\"specialty\" width=\"748\" height=\"269\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225664\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/specialty.jpg 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/specialty-300x108.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If your niche involves you finding jobs for others, we have what you need with the Specialty theme. This theme comes with a fully responsive layout that gives you access to all the tools you need to build a wonderful, professional job board. </p>\n<p>You can add search features for those looking for specific jobs, create subcategories, upload stories to your blog, and more. Specialty gives you full control of your website without the use of complicated coding and micromanaging.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-specialty/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Specialty Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best WordPress themes for membership sites.</p>\n<p>If you found this post useful, you might also enjoy our comparison of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared (2018)\">9 best email marketing services</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-membership-sites/\">24 Best WordPress Themes for Membership Sites (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-membership-sites/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"7 Best Download Manager Plugins Compared (Fast &amp; Secure)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-download-manager-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-download-manager-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 11 Dec 2018 10:23:44 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"download manager\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"free and premium plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=224885\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:629:\"<p>Are you looking for the best download manager plugins for WordPress? Good idea! While WordPress websites allow you to upload files and place download links in your posts and pages, there’s no default way to scale them. Whereas, with a download manager plugin, you can track, manage, and control permissions for your file downloads. You [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-download-manager-plugins/\">7 Best Download Manager Plugins Compared (Fast &#038; Secure)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13632:\"<p>Are you looking for the best download manager plugins for WordPress? Good idea! While WordPress websites allow you to upload files and place download links in your posts and pages, there’s no default way to scale them. Whereas, with a download manager plugin, you can track, manage, and control permissions for your file downloads. You can even use them to SELL file downloads, if you wish!</p>\n<p>That’s why, in this article, we’ve handpicked the 7 best download manager plugins for WordPress! Check them out, choose your perfect match, and get ready to love the results.</p>\n<h3>Choosing the Best WordPress Download Manager Plugin</h3>\n<p>There are different types of download manager plugins. While some plugins let you track file downloads on your WordPress site, others provide secure access to files. </p>\n<p>Just because you’re offering file downloads on your site, doesn’t mean you need all sort of download manager plugins. Before you dive in and choose a download manager for your site, it’s essential for you to examine the purpose, so you don’t waste your money on the wrong plugin. </p>\n<p>Ask yourself a few questions. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Do you need to track WordPress downloads?</li>\n<li>Do you want to provide a secure access to the file?</li>\n<li>Do you want to sync your files to Dropbox or Google Drive?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now that you’ve got a basic idea, let’s go ahead and view the top 7 download manager plugins for WordPress. </p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-6\">At a Glance: 7 Best Download Manager Plugins</h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-6\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-6\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1 odd\">\n	<th class=\"column-1\">Plugin</th><th class=\"column-2\">Price</th><th class=\"column-3\">Active Installs</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-2 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">From $79.60/year</td><td class=\"column-3\">Over 2 million</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wordpress-file-download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress File Download Manager</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$17</td><td class=\"column-3\">1,400+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/multiverso-advanced-file-sharing-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Multiverso</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">$30</td><td class=\"column-3\">1,100+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Easy Digital Downloads</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">60,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress Download Manager</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">100,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7 odd\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-attachments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download Attachments</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">10,000+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-8 even\">\n	<td class=\"column-1\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/delightful-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Delightful Downloads</a></td><td class=\"column-2\">Free</td><td class=\"column-3\">10,000+</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- #tablepress-6 from cache -->\n<h3><a href=\"https://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\">1. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221490\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-plugin-wordpress-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights is number 1 on this list for good reason. Not only is it the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-analytics-solutions-compared/\">best Google Analytics tool</a> on the market, it’s also the best download manager plugin for WordPress.</p>\n<p>With just a few clicks, you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/google-analytics-ecommerce-tracking-woocommerce/\">set up Google Analytics on your WordPress website</a> and get access to things like real-time stats, eCommerce tracking, ads tracking, referral tracking, popular posts tracking, forms tracking, and more! It’s GDPR compliant, won’t slow down your site, and all the reports you need can be accessed from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p>Now, with the File Downloads Tracking addon, you can utilize MonsterInsights as a download manager plugin as well! Need help getting started? Check out our tutorial on how to set up download tracking in Google Analytics using Monster Insights.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with MonsterInsights Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wordpress-file-download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. WordPress File Download Manager</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wordpress-file-download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-File-Download-Manager.jpg\" alt=\"WordPress File Download Manager\" width=\"694\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225026\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-File-Download-Manager.jpg 694w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-File-Download-Manager-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 694px) 100vw, 694px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Need to give your clients access to confidential files in a secure way? Then the WordPress File Download Manager is the plugin for you.</p>\n<p>Your WordPress site users can login and download the files you’ve assigned specifically to them. Even if the file download is a URL, this highly secured plugin will ensure that only the assigned user can download the file.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wordpress-file-download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with WordPress File Download Manager Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/multiverso-advanced-file-sharing-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Multiverso Advanced File Sharing</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/multiverso-advanced-file-sharing-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Multiverso.jpg\" alt=\"Multiverso\" width=\"697\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225027\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Multiverso.jpg 697w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Multiverso-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 697px) 100vw, 697px\" /></a></p>\n<p>An advanced file sharing plugin with developer-friendly features, Multiverso lets you create a file sharing section on your WordPress website that’s accessible to the user roles you allow, from administrators to subscribers.</p>\n<p>Set your security checks, file upload size, categories, and more. There’s also plenty of shortcodes as well as sexy jQuery options.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/multiverso-advanced-file-sharing-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Multiverso Advanced File Sharing Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Easy Digital Downloads</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Easy-Digital-Downloads.jpg\" alt=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" width=\"775\" height=\"190\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225028\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Easy-Digital-Downloads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Easy-Digital-Downloads-300x74.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Easy-Digital-Downloads-768x188.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’ve got an eCommerce website and you’re selling digital downloads, then Easy Digital Downloads is the perfect plugin for you. You can track anything from eBooks, to photos, to documents, to songs with this complete selling system.</p>\n<p>Available in over 24 languages, EDD makes it easy to jump into selling and managing your downloads, no matter where you are in the world. </p>\n<p>This free plugin integrates with PayPal, Amazon Payments, Stripe, Authorize.net, BitPay, and more. Need even more options? Their premium extensions give you access to even more payment gateways, email service integrations, and file management options.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Easy Digital Downloads Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. WordPress Download Manager</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-Download-Manager.jpg\" alt=\"WordPress Download Manager\" width=\"775\" height=\"281\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225029\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-Download-Manager.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-Download-Manager-300x109.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WordPress-Download-Manager-768x278.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Manage, track, and take complete control of your file downloads with the WordPress Download Manager plugin. Keep your files secure by assigning them to user roles, or by setting passwords.</p>\n<p>For eCommerce sites, there are options to set up licenses, prices, download limits, and more. It also integrates with DropBox, OneDrive, Google Drive, and more.</p>\n<p>Secure and translation-ready, this free plugin is easy to set up and use with multiple useful features.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Download Manager Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-attachments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Download Attachments</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-attachments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Download-Attachments.jpg\" alt=\"Download Attachments\" width=\"775\" height=\"278\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225030\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Download-Attachments.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Download-Attachments-300x108.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Download-Attachments-768x275.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Download Attachments is one of the best download manager plugins because it makes use of AJAX and a simple drag and drop interface. We love simplicity.</p>\n<p>However, if you’re a developer and wish to expand Download Attachments’ features, you’ll love their multiple filter hooks and functions.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/download-attachments/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Download Attachments Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/delightful-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Delightful Downloads</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/delightful-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Delightful-Downloads.jpg\" alt=\"Delightful Downloads\" width=\"775\" height=\"261\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225031\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Delightful-Downloads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Delightful-Downloads-300x101.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Delightful-Downloads-768x259.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This developer-friendly plugin is free to download and use, and lets you easily add download buttons and links to pages, posts, and wigetized areas.</p>\n<p>Best of all, your download statistics and reports can be found directly inside your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/delightful-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Delightful Downloads Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best download manager plugins for WordPress.</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this post, you might also like our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-security-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 Best WordPress Security Plugins Compared (2018)\">6 best WordPress security plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-download-manager-plugins/\">7 Best Download Manager Plugins Compared (Fast &#038; Secure)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-download-manager-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"How to Set Up Shopify with WordPress (Step by Step)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 10 Dec 2018 10:01:22 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"how to create an online store\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"how to integrate shopify with wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"how to start an online store\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=225323\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:609:\"<p>Are you wondering how to integrate Shopify with WordPress? For WordPress beginners, it might seem difficult to turn your WordPress site into an online store, but it&#8217;s not. Starting an online shop is easier than ever before with Shopify and WordPress. Anyone can build a beautiful online shop in no time and start selling right [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/\">How to Set Up Shopify with WordPress (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22700:\"<p>Are you wondering how to integrate Shopify with WordPress? For WordPress beginners, it might seem difficult to turn your WordPress site into an online store, but it&#8217;s not. Starting an online shop is easier than ever before with Shopify and WordPress. Anyone can build a beautiful online shop in no time and start selling right away, without knowing a thing about code. </p>\n<p>So, are you ready to build your own online store and start selling immediately? </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to integrate Shopify with WordPress, step-by-step. </p>\n<h3>Why Integrate Shopify with WordPress?</h3>\n<p>WordPress offers several <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\">eCommerce plugins</a>, like WooCommerce, to help you start an online shop. </p>\n<p>Maybe you&#8217;re wondering why you should choose <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target =\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shopify</a> over the other eCommerce plugins? Below are a few advantages of using Shopify as your storefront:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Ease of use </strong>: Getting started with Shopify is much easier than using native WordPress eCommerce plugins. All you have to do is <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target =\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">sign up for an account with Shopify</a> to get your online shop up and running. You also don&#8217;t have to worry about site speed or security, because Shopify takes care of all of that for you.</li>\n<li><strong>Reduced overhead</strong>: Shopify is a cloud-based solution, so you won&#8217;t experience traffic outages as your business grows. This means you don&#8217;t have to worry about running out of server resources and upgrading to more expensive WordPress hosting.</li>\n<li><strong>Easy social media integration</strong>: Integrating your online store with social media is important for marketing your business and products. Shopify&#8217;s app store makes it easy. They have apps to integrate your Instagram feed on your site, add social media sharing buttons, and more. All you have to do is download the apps of your choosing, no coding required. </li>\n<li><strong>Better shopping cart options</strong>: Shopify offers built-in payment options so you can instantly take payments from Visa, Mastercard, Discover, and American Express. They also offer multiple payment gateways like PayPal, and they&#8217;ll automatically calculate shipping rates and taxes for you so you can easily ship to anywhere in the world.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Who Should Use Shopify with WordPress?</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Shopify</a> is a good choice for online selling beginners and experienced sellers alike. But Shopify is especially great for beginners because it&#8217;s a lot easier to use. Unlike WooCommerce, you don&#8217;t have to install anything and you can get started quickly. </p>\n<p>They also have easy-to-understand pricing plans. Shopify&#8217;s basic plan starts at $29 per month. You don&#8217;t have to worry about spending too much money on hosting plans and optimization for your online store. With their basic plan, you can minimize the risks of starting an online shop. And, as your online business grows, you can upgrade your plan to match your needs. </p>\n<p>Shopify is the platform for you if you want a solution that&#8217;s completely <strong>hassle-free</strong> and is <strong>limitless in terms of scalability</strong> for your online shop. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-logo-1.jpg\" alt=\"how to add shopify to wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"319\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225360\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-logo-1.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-logo-1-300x129.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;d still rather use WooCommerce with WordPress, check out our tutorial: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\">How to Create an Online Store with WooCommerce- Step-by-Step</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s dive into how to integrate Shopify with WordPress.   </p>\n<h3>Set Up Shopify with WordPress &#8211; Step-by-Step</h3>\n<p>Integrating <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target =\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shopify</a> with your WordPress site is as easy as embedding the code snippet. Let&#8217;s take a look at the step-by-step guide below. </p>\n<h3>Step 0: Start a Website on WordPress</h3>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t already have a WordPress website, you&#8217;ll need to create one in order to start an online shop with Shopify. WordPress is the most popular website builder in the world, it&#8217;s the best platform to start a website. It comes with a number of built-in features that&#8217;ll help you easily build a website without having to know anything about code. </p>\n<p>There&#8217;re a number of steps to starting a website on WordPress. First, you&#8217;ll need to pick a domain name for your business. A domain name, or URL, is your site&#8217;s address online. We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.nameboy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Nameboy</a> to help find the perfect domain name for your online shop. </p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll need to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-hosting/\">choose a website host</a>. A web host is the business that provides the technologies and services a website needs to be viewed on the internet. It&#8217;s where your website files are stored. In other words, if your domain name is your address; your web hosting is your house.</p>\n<p>We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Bluehost</a> to set up your online store. Bluehost is one of the best website hosting services available and they offer 1-click WordPress installation so you can create your online shop super fast.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluehost-wordpress.png\" alt=\"start-a-website-bluehost\" width=\"740\" height=\"419\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225328\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluehost-wordpress.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/bluehost-wordpress-300x170.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve negotiated a deal with Bluehost to offer our users a free domain name, free SSL, and over 60% off on WordPress hosting.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>If you want more detailed instructions on how to start a website on WordPress, check out our tutorial on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">how to make a website &#8211; step-by-step</a>. </p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve got a domain name, a web hosting, installed WordPress, and built your website, you&#8217;re ready to integrate Shopify and start selling.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Set up a Shopify Store</h3>\n<p>The first step to integrating Shopify with WordPress is to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target =\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">set up an account with Shopify</a>. Head over to the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Shopify</a> website. On their home page, you&#8217;ll see an area where you can enter your email address to start a free 14-day trial. After typing in your email address, press the <strong>Get Started</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-get-started-2.png\" alt=\"set-up-shopify-account\" width=\"740\" height=\"238\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225331\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-get-started-2.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-get-started-2-300x96.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll be prompted to choose a password for you account and your store name as well. When you&#8217;ve finished entering in the information, click on the <strong>Create your store</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-password.png\" alt=\"how-to-integrate-shopify-with-wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"413\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225334\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-password.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-password-300x167.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Then, you&#8217;ll be asked to answer a couple questions from Shopify so they can get to know your needs better. Click on the dropdown arrow to choose your answers to the questions and then click <strong>Next</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up1.png\" alt=\"set-up-shopify-with-wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"447\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225335\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up1.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up1-300x181.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>In the next area, you&#8217;ll be requested to fill in your name, address, phone number, and website address. When you&#8217;ve finished filling out this part, click the <strong>Enter my store</strong> button at the bottom of the form. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up2.png\" alt=\"setting-up-shopify-account\" width=\"740\" height=\"534\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225336\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up2.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-set-up2-300x216.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll then be redirected to the home page of your Shopify account. Your Shopify store is now ready for you. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-dashboard.png\" alt=\"shopify-dashboard\" width=\"740\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225338\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-dashboard.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-dashboard-300x144.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-dashboard-330x160.png 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<h3>Step 2: Set up Payments and Shipping for Your Shopify Store</h3>\n<p>In order to accept payments from customers, you&#8217;ll need to set up payments for your Shopify store. To do so, click on <strong>Settings</strong> in the bottom corner of your home page and then click on <strong>Payment providers</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payments.png\" alt=\"shopify-set-up-payments\" width=\"740\" height=\"329\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225340\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payments.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payments-300x133.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Your Shopify account is automatically set up to receive PayPal payments with PayPal Express Checkout. If you have a PayPal account set up already with the email address you used to create your Shopify account, you should be ready to accept payments. If you don&#8217;t have a PayPal account, Shopify will send you an email with instructions on how to set up a PayPal Merchant account to claim your funds.   </p>\n<p>For the ability to accept other forms of payment from customers like credit cards, you&#8217;ll need to click on the <strong>Complete account setup</strong> button to provide Shopify with more details about your business. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payment-providers.png\" alt=\"how-to-set-up-shopify-payments\" width=\"740\" height=\"380\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225344\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payment-providers.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-payment-providers-300x154.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also choose to accept alternative forms of payment like BitPay and GoCoin as well.</p>\n<p>The last step to setting up your Shopify store so it&#8217;s ready to start selling is to set up shipping. Click on the <strong>Settings</strong> button again and then click on <strong>Shipping</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-shipping.png\" alt=\"shopify-shipping-set-up\" width=\"740\" height=\"325\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225345\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-shipping.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-shipping-300x132.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>By default, the shipping origin will be set to the store address you entered in when setting up your Shopify account. You can edit the shipping origin if you wish by clicking the <strong>Change shipping origin</strong> button. </p>\n<p>In this area, you can also define shipping zones and rates for shipping to those locations. If you don&#8217;t know how much to charge for shipping, try contacting your local post office to get some advice. </p>\n<h3>Step 3: Add Your Products to Shopify</h3>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll need to add your products to your Spotify account. To add your products, click on the <strong>Products</strong> tab in the menu on the right and then click on <strong>Add product</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-products.png\" alt=\"add products to shopify\" width=\"740\" height=\"320\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225356\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-products.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-products-300x130.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Then fill out all of the information about your product including the name/title of your product, product description, price, and more. Upload a high-quality image of your product here as well. You can also add the product to a collection to make it easier to find in your store. When you&#8217;re finished filling in all of the details for your product, click the <strong>Save</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-addproduct.png\" alt=\"add-products-to-your-shopify-account\" width=\"740\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225357\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-addproduct.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-addproduct-300x156.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Repeat this step for all of the products you offer. </p>\n<h3>Step 4: Choosing Your Shopify Pricing Plan</h3>\n<p>Now that you&#8217;ve got the basics of your Shopify account configured, you&#8217;ll have to choose a pricing plan to actually get your online store up and running. Click on the <strong>Select a plan</strong> button in the banner at the bottom of your screen.  </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan.png\" alt=\"shopify-plan\" width=\"740\" height=\"397\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225352\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan-300x161.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll then be presented with 3 different plan options. If you&#8217;re just starting out and new to selling online, we recommend choosing the Basic Shopify plan for $29 per month. You can always upgrade your plan anytime you want if you need more features or if your online store grows quickly. To choose the Basic Shopify plan, click the <strong>Choose this plan</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan2.png\" alt=\"setting up shopify with wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"445\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225354\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan2.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-plan2-300x180.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Then enter your credit card information and press the <strong>Start plan</strong> button.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with Shopify Today!</a> </p>\n<p>Now you&#8217;re ready to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\" target=\"_blank\">start making money online</a> with Shopify and your WordPress site. </p>\n<h3>Step 5: Using Shopify Buy Button</h3>\n<p>Now it&#8217;s time to integrate Shopify with your WordPress site with Buy Buttons. Buy Buttons link to your Shopify checkout and they&#8217;re included in all Shopify plans. Buy Buttons allow you to sell your products on your website or in blog posts. You can also use Buy Buttons to create a checkout link to send to customers in email messages or on social media. </p>\n<p>If the Buy Button sales channel doesn&#8217;t appear in the Sales Channel section of your Shopify admin, you&#8217;ll need to add it. To add the Buy Button sales channel, click on <strong>Settings</strong> and then click on the <strong>Sales channels</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-sales-channel.png\" alt=\"adding shopify to wordpress with buy button\" width=\"740\" height=\"332\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225358\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-sales-channel.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-sales-channel-300x135.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the <strong>Add sales channel</strong> button. You&#8217;ll then see a list of available sales channels, scroll down to find the <strong>Buy Button</strong> channel. Once you find it, click the blue <strong>+</strong> button to install. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-add-buybutton.png\" alt=\"how to install buy button to integrate shopify and wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"402\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225359\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-add-buybutton.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-add-buybutton-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>After installing the Buy Button sales channel, click on the <strong>Create Buy Button</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-create-buy-button.png\" alt=\"create shopify buy button\" width=\"740\" height=\"373\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225361\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-create-buy-button.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-create-buy-button-300x151.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, pick the product you want to create a buy button for and click the <strong>Select product</strong> button. Now you can configure the look of your Buy Button. You can choose a template, customize the button color and text, and the action that happens when a customer clicks the button. When you&#8217;re finished customizing the appearance of your button, click the <strong>Generate code</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-buy-button-creation-.png\" alt=\"shopify product buy button for wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"589\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225362\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-buy-button-creation-.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-buy-button-creation--300x239.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>The next step is to copy the code and add it to your WordPress site. </p>\n<h3>Step 6: Add Shopify Buy Buttons to Your WordPress Site</h3>\n<p>Now we need to add your products to your WordPress site so you can start selling them. Click the <strong>Copy code to clipboard</strong> button to copy the code you just generated for that product. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-generate-code.png\" alt=\"add-shopify-product-to-wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"409\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225363\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-generate-code.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-generate-code-300x166.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You can paste this code anywhere on your website where you want your Buy Button to appear. For example, you can create a page on your WordPress site to display your Buy Buttons. Create the page on WordPress, name it, and then paste the code. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-wordpress.png\" alt=\"how to add shopify buy buttons to wordpress\" width=\"740\" height=\"408\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225364\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-wordpress.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/shopify-wordpress-300x165.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also paste the code in <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/50-blog-post-ideas-that-you-can-write-about-today/\" target=\"_blank\">blog posts</a> or in your WordPress sidebar. </p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! Integrating Shopify with WordPress is that easy. Now that you know how to add Shopify to your WordPress site, you&#8217;ll be attracting customers and making a ton of sales in no time.</p>\n<p>We hope you enjoyed this article. If you did, take a look at our article on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\">9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, Fast!</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/\">How to Set Up Shopify with WordPress (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"AffiliateWP Review – Affiliate Program for WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 07 Dec 2018 11:20:14 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=225678\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:615:\"<p>Looking to create an affiliate program for your product? An affiliate program is a referral system where you incentivize others to refer your product by offering them a commission for every sale they refer. How do you create an affiliate system in WordPress? That’s what the AffiliateWP plugin was created for. It enables you to [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/\">AffiliateWP Review – Affiliate Program for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22879:\"<p>Looking to create an affiliate program for your product? An affiliate program is a referral system where you incentivize others to refer your product by offering them a commission for every sale they refer.</p>\n<p>How do you create an affiliate system in WordPress? That’s what the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> plugin was created for. It enables you to create a full-fledged affiliate system in WordPress with ease. If you want to know more about its features, functionalities, pricing, etc., continue reading our complete AffiliateWP review below. </p>\n<h3>About the AffiliateWP Plugin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"427\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225686\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress-300x165.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-best-affiliate-management-system-for-wordpress-768x423.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> is the #1 affiliate management system plugin for WordPress. It allows you to build a complete affiliate system in WordPress and helps to manage affiliates, referrals, payments, etc. from your site. It comes with all the affiliate marketing tools you&#8217;ll need to grow your business and earn money. </p>\n<p>It’s a plugin built for WordPress that looks and feels like WordPress itself. All of its features are carefully-designed to adapt with WordPress and to give you a familiar experience. Plus, it comes with advanced affiliate and referral tracking features that provide reliable, accurate data. </p>\n<p>AffiliateWP was developed by the same team who created the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Easy Digital Downloads</a> eCoommerce plugin. Therefore, the plugin has seamless integration with Easy Digital Downloads. Not to mention, it also has full support for WooCommerce and other popular membership, form, and invoice plugins. </p>\n<h3>How Does Affiliate Marketing Work?</h3>\n<p>Affiliate marketing is one of the most popular ways to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\">make money online</a>. Affiliate marketing creates a win-win situation for the 2 parties involved; the business owners and the affiliates. It’s the collaboration in which affiliates help to sell more products and business owners offer a commission to affiliates for each sale they referred to. </p>\n<p>For example, if you’re a business owner and trying to sell products, you can create an affiliate system on your site and appeal affiliates to join. When they become an affiliate of your website, they pick products from your store and promote them on their blog and various other platforms. Now if people come to your store via the affiliate links and buy a product, the affiliate who referred the customer gets a certain percent commission. </p>\n<p>As a business owner, your store will get more visibility, more traffic, and more sales. On the other hand, affiliates will earn money for each sale they referred to your store. Therefore, it’s rewarding to both businesses and affiliate marketers. </p>\n<p>So, if you’re running an online store but don’t have an affiliate program, you definitely need to consider having one. </p>\n<h3>AffiliateWP Review – Getting Started with AffiliateWP</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> is a plugin exclusively designed for WordPress with an interface just like the native WordPress interface. It’s therefore easy to configure and use. </p>\n<p>First, download the plugin file from the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">official AffiliateWP website</a> and install it on your site. If you need detailed instructions, here’s our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\">how to install a plugin</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>1. General Settings</strong></p>\n<p>After the plugin is activated, navigate to <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Settings</strong> to activate your plugin license. You can find the license key in your account on the AffiliteWP website. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-general-setting.jpg\" alt=\"affiliatewp-general-setting\" width=\"775\" height=\"387\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225687\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-general-setting.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-general-setting-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-general-setting-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>In addition to license activation, the <strong>General</strong> tab has a number of affiliate settings. You can select an affiliate page or affiliate agreement page; however, feel free to leave them as they are because these pages are automatically created by the plugin to meet affiliate-specific needs. </p>\n<p>Next, you can configure referral settings. The referral variable by default is <strong>ref</strong> and the default referral format looks like this: <strong>https://yoursite.com/?ref=1</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-settings.jpg\" alt=\"referral-settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"223\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225688\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-settings-300x86.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-settings-768x221.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to change the referral variable, you can use <strong>aff, refer, partner</strong>, etc. </p>\n<p>Next, you can enable <strong>Pretty Affiliate URLs</strong> which will replace the query strings (i.e. ?ref=) and change your URL format to <strong>https://yoursite.com/ref/1</strong>.</p>\n<p>You can select a referral rate type from either a percentage or a flat amount. Then, you can add a referral rate. Also review <strong>Exclude Shipping</strong> and <strong>Exclude Tax</strong> options. Then, you can also add a cookie expiration duration; for example, 30 days (which means that a purchase within 30 days of user’s visit via a referral link will be valid for the commission). </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review.jpg\" alt=\"referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review\" width=\"775\" height=\"387\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225689\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referral-rate-settings-affiliatewp-review-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once you review all the options, don’t forget to click <strong>Save Changes</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>2. Integrations</strong></p>\n<p>The plugin has inbuilt integration for a number of eCommerce, membership, form, and invoice plugins and systems. You can enable the ones you need easily from <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Settings &raquo; Integrations</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/integrations-affiliatewp-settings.jpg\" alt=\"integrations-affiliatewp-settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225690\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/integrations-affiliatewp-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/integrations-affiliatewp-settings-300x271.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/integrations-affiliatewp-settings-768x694.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>3. Email Settings</strong></p>\n<p>You can configure all the email settings from the <strong>Email</strong> tab in AffiliateWP settings. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/email-settings-affiliatewp.jpg\" alt=\"email-settings-affiliatewp\" width=\"775\" height=\"700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225691\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/email-settings-affiliatewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/email-settings-affiliatewp-300x271.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/email-settings-affiliatewp-768x694.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can upload a logo, choose an email template, from name and email, etc. Then, you can configure notification emails on new affiliate registrations, affiliate application accepted, referral awarded, affiliate application being reviewed, and application rejected. </p>\n<p><strong>4. Miscellaneous Settings</strong></p>\n<p>The <strong>Misc</strong> tab in AffiliateWP settings allow you to configure different options useful for your affiliate system. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/misc-settings-affiliatewp.jpg\" alt=\"misc-settings-affiliatewp\" width=\"775\" height=\"386\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225692\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/misc-settings-affiliatewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/misc-settings-affiliatewp-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/misc-settings-affiliatewp-768x383.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can enable or disable affiliate registration by the user themselves, affiliate approval required, reCAPTCHA, and much more. </p>\n<p>Review all the settings, and then click <strong>Save Changes</strong> to save your settings. </p>\n<h3>Creating the Affiliate Area</h3>\n<p>Affiliate Area is where your users can see the affiliate registration and login form. Via this page, new affiliate marketers apply for your affiliate program whereas already signed-up affiliates can log into their accounts, generate referral links, view stats, and see their earnings. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP plugin</a> automatically creates an <strong>Affiliate Area</strong> page right when you install the plugin into WordPress. If you don’t find this page, you can create a new page yourself and add the shortcode <strong>[affiliate_area]</strong> in the main content area, then it’ll create the affiliate area page for you. </p>\n<p>Take a look at the screenshot below to see how your Affiliate Area will look: </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area\" width=\"268\" height=\"700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225693\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area.jpg 268w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-115x300.jpg 115w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 268px) 100vw, 268px\" /></p>\n<p>When a user logs into their account, they’ll see a different Affiliate Area. The Affiliate Area for logged-in users looks like the screenshot below: </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp.jpg\" alt=\"aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp\" width=\"775\" height=\"689\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225694\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp-300x267.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/aff-area-url-generator-affiliatewp-768x683.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Affiliates can generate affiliate URLs by entering a page URL in the field there and clicking on the <strong>Generate URL</strong> button. </p>\n<p>Next, the <strong>Statistics</strong> option shows a summary of paid and unpaid referrals, visits, conversion rate, earnings, and commission rates. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-statistics.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-statistics\" width=\"775\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225695\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-statistics.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-statistics-300x223.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-statistics-768x570.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Upon clicking on the next option, <strong>Graphs</strong>, affiliates can see a graphical presentation of the affiliate statistics. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-graphs.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-graphs\" width=\"775\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225696\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-graphs.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-graphs-300x223.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-graphs-768x570.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Referrals</strong> provides a glimpse of the affiliate’s referrals with the amount earned, product description, and status as paid or unpaid.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-referrals.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-referrals\" width=\"775\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225697\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-referrals.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-referrals-300x223.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-referrals-768x570.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The <strong>Visits</strong> option shows the pages visited by their affiliate links. </p>\n<p>The <strong>Creatives</strong> option includes promotional banners which affiliates can use on their blogs and multiple other platforms to promote your products.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-creatives.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-creatives\" width=\"775\" height=\"700\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225698\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-creatives.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-creatives-300x271.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-creatives-768x694.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>And, finally, the <strong>Settings</strong> tab lets your affiliates add their payment email where you can send the commissions they earn.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-settings.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-area-settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"433\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225699\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-settings-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliate-area-settings-768x429.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The Affiliate Area looks very clean and simple. Affiliate marketers will love your affiliate program interface. </p>\n<h3>Managing Your Affiliate Program</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> provides you with simple-yet-powerful options to manage your affiliate program. You can add, edit, and review affiliates; view individual and total affiliate reports; manage referrals, visits, and creative aspects; and view full reports on everything. </p>\n<p>Configuring and managing the admin options is easy with AffiliateWP. To get started, you can take a look at the overview of your affiliate system by going to <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Overview</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/admin-overview-affiliatewp.jpg\" alt=\"admin-overview-affiliatewp\" width=\"775\" height=\"386\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225700\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/admin-overview-affiliatewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/admin-overview-affiliatewp-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/admin-overview-affiliatewp-768x383.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can see the totals for paid earnings, unpaid referrals, most valuable affiliates, latest affiliate registrations, recent referrals, etc. in the Overview. </p>\n<p>Next, you can go to <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Affiliate</strong> to view your list of all affiliates, add new affiliates, edit, etc. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"386\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225701\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliates-affiliatewp-plugin-768x383.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The entire affiliate management works just like standard posts in WordPress. </p>\n<h3>AffiliateWP Addons</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP plugin</a> comes with powerful free and premium addons which you can use to make your affiliate program more effective. In addition, it also supports a number of third-party addons. </p>\n<p>There’re 15 official free addons and 14 pro addons. The pro addons include PayPal Payouts, Recurring Referrals, Lifetime Commissions, Affiliate Landing Pages, etc. The free addons allow you to add features like display a leaderboard, showing attributed affiliate coupons, pay affiliates with store credit, etc. </p>\n<p>You can access the addons from your WordPress dashboard by visiting <strong>Affiliates &raquo; Addons</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-addons.jpg\" alt=\"affiliatewp-addons\" width=\"775\" height=\"619\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225702\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-addons.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-addons-300x240.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-addons-768x613.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<h3>AffiliateWP Plugin: Pricing and Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> is a premium plugin that offers 4 pricing plans. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-pricing.jpg\" alt=\"affiliatewp-pricing\" width=\"775\" height=\"308\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225703\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-pricing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-pricing-300x119.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/affiliatewp-pricing-768x305.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>1. Personal</strong>: It costs $99 per year. You can use it on 1 website only. Includes 15 official free addons and all AffiliateWP&#8217;s core features. </p>\n<p><strong>2. Plus</strong>: It costs $149 per year. It provides 3 site licenses. It also includes all free addons and core features of the plugin.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Professional</strong>: It costs $249 per year. You can use AffiliateWP on unlimited sites with this plan. It includes all 15 pro addons along with all the free official addons. </p>\n<p><strong>4. Ultimate</strong>: It’s priced at $499 and it’s a one-time payment plan. With this plan, you can use AffiliateWP on unlimited sites. It also includes all pro and free addons and also future addons. </p>\n<p>With the 3 yearly subscription plans, you’ll get email support and updates for the duration of your current subscription whereas you’ll get lifetime support and updates with the <strong>Ultimate</strong> plan. </p>\n<p>If you have any questions, you can use their live chat for instant replies. You can also submit a ticket for support queries but you may not need to contact support because they have detailed documentation with really comprehensive articles to guide you. </p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using AffiliateWP for Creating a Affiliate System in WordPress</h3>\n<p>AffiliateWP is undoubtedly the number 1 best affiliate management system plugin for WordPress. It has a complete set of features and functionalities to allow you to create a powerful affiliate system in WordPress. Its integration with eCommerce, membership, forms, and invoice plugins make it the all-in-one solution for affiliate programs. </p>\n<p>The plugin was created just for WordPress which makes it a very special product. Its interface is very similar to the WordPress interface so anyone using WordPress will recognize the familiar feel of it and configure everything very easily. It’s a simple plugin that you can use without touching any code. </p>\n<p>We believe that <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/affiliatewp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> is the best affiliate management plugin for creating and running an affiliate program on WordPress sites. It’s a great tool you can use to boost your sales, improve SEO, and grow your business. </p>\n<p>We give it 4.5 out of 5 stars. Here’s the breakdown of our review score:</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/\">AffiliateWP Review – Affiliate Program for WordPress</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/affiliatewp/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"21 Best WordPress Real Estate Themes for 2018 (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-themes/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 06 Dec 2018 10:04:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"real estate themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"realtor themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"wordpress real estate\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=224052\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:610:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress real estate themes? The real estate business is highly competitive, and sometimes all it takes to get ahead of the game is a great-looking website! However, while that sounds simple enough in theory, it can take weeks to look through the thousands of themes available to find your [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-themes/\">21 Best WordPress Real Estate Themes for 2018 (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26783:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress real estate themes? The real estate business is highly competitive, and sometimes all it takes to get ahead of the game is a great-looking website! However, while that sounds simple enough in theory, it can take weeks to look through the thousands of themes available to find your perfect match.</p>\n<p>That’s why we’ve handpicked the 21 best real estate themes for WordPress just for you. Now you can stop worrying about choosing a theme and get back to what you do best!</p>\n<p>Bonus: all of the themes listed are mobile responsive, so your real estate website will look gorgeous on any device.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-agentpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. AgentPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-agentpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/agentpress-pro-1.jpg\" alt=\"agentpress-pro\" width=\"740\" height=\"473\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225353\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/agentpress-pro-1.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/agentpress-pro-1-300x192.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Brought to you by StudioPress, AgentPress runs on their famous Genesis framework. It’s exactly what you’re looking for if “savvy” is the word you use to describe your business.</p>\n<p>AgentPress comes with its own listings management plugin, allowing you to create custom widgets, taxonomies, and post types. You can also customize the header so that your site perfectly matches your brand.</p>\n<p>Speaking of customization, you can alter the theme’s settings and color schemes as well. Plus, it has 6 homepage widget areas!</p>\n<p>This theme is easy to set up and start using, and even includes a live preview option to see your changes in real time.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-agentpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with AgentPress Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-realtor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Realtor</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-realtor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/realtor.png\" alt=\"realtor\" width=\"740\" height=\"436\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225349\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/realtor.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/realtor-300x177.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Whether you’re on your own or part of an agency, Realtor is definitely one of the best WordPress real estate themes. It’s clean, modern, and ultra-stylish.</p>\n<p>You’re going to love its advanced property filters and search functions, and so will your customers. It even integrates with Google Maps’ API to create its own properties map.</p>\n<p>It’s super easy to list and sell properties with Realtor. The image upload function is buttery smooth, and we loved that you could customize the style of each individual property page.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-realtor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Realtor Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/agentevolution-mustsee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. MustSee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/agentevolution-mustsee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/must-see.png\" alt=\"must see\" width=\"740\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225348\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/must-see.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/must-see-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With its parallax scrolling photo background, MustSee is a classic website theme with a modern twist.</p>\n<p>You can choose from 4 color schemes to customize MustSee to your personal style. Plus, it was built on the Equity Framework, made specifically for realtors, for extra oomph.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/agentevolution-mustsee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with MustSee Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-estate-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. EstateEngine</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-estate-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/EstateEngine.png\" alt=\"EstateEngine\" width=\"707\" height=\"245\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224057\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/EstateEngine.png 707w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/EstateEngine-300x104.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 707px) 100vw, 707px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This theme has everything you’d expect from a real estate website and then some! It has numerous advanced functions that are all fairly easy to use, for both you and your potential clients.</p>\n<p>The search function is top-of-the-line, and EstateEngine makes it easy to upload properties and have clients submit properties. It’s also incredibly simple to monetize thanks to payment plans and ad options.</p>\n<p>We love that EstateEngine comes with its own drag and drop builder, making it effortless to customize.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-estate-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Estate Engine Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-residence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Residence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-residence/ \" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/residence.jpg\" alt=\"residence\" width=\"775\" height=\"317\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224058\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/residence.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/residence-300x123.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/residence-768x314.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sleek and silver, Residence gives off an air of luxury. If you’re looking for high-end clients, this theme is a great way to showcase your most valuable properties.</p>\n<p>Residence comes with dsIDXPress plugin integration, allowing your potential clients to search through the MLS with ease. We also appreciated that it comes preloaded with nearly every currency symbol you could ever need, making it easy to price your listings no matter where you are in the world.</p>\n<p>This theme also works equally well if you have multiple agents on your team. Residence gives each agent their own admin dashboard.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-residence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Residence Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-oikia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Oikia</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-oikia/ \" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/oikia.jpg\" alt=\"oikia\" width=\"754\" height=\"256\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224059\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/oikia.jpg 754w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/oikia-300x102.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 754px) 100vw, 754px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Search engine optimized and loaded with its own drag and drop builder, Oikia is incredibly easy to customize. There are widgets available for nearly everything, including social media links, content blocks, maps, and more!</p>\n<p>One of the best features included with Oikia is the ability to choose a different color scheme for each of your pages.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-oikia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Oikia Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-elviria/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Elviria</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-elviria/ \" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elviria.png\" alt=\"elviria\" width=\"650\" height=\"236\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224060\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elviria.png 650w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/elviria-300x109.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Choose 1 of 2 pre-built home pages, add your own content, and get ready to sell! Elviria makes it easy to get your website running in a snap.</p>\n<p>Rather than the usual sidebar and footer widget areas, Elviria has options to add widget-ready areas to multiple sections of your website. This, along with its unlimited color scheme options, make it highly customizable.</p>\n<p>The listings carousel and image gallery options also add extra appeal to your site, enticing potential clients with eye-catching graphic effects.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-elviria/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Elviria Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-bahia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Bahia</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-bahia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/balia.png\" alt=\"bahia\" width=\"719\" height=\"444\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225351\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/balia.png 719w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/balia-300x185.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 719px) 100vw, 719px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Customization is key with the Bahia theme. You’re going to love how easy it is to match your theme to your brand once you get started with this one.</p>\n<p>With unlimited color options and a custom header area, Bahia can be personalized in just a few clicks of your mouse.</p>\n<p>Plus, like its sister theme, Elviria, Bahia also includes a listings carousel and image gallery options.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-bahia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Bahia Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-london/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. London</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-london/ \" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/london.jpg\" alt=\"london\" width=\"775\" height=\"183\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224062\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/london.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/london-300x71.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/london-768x181.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Flexible widget areas, unlimited color options, and a highly customizable header area are all part of what makes London one of the best real estate themes for WordPress.</p>\n<p>London comes with a ton of custom widgets including image sliders, featured content boxes, newsletter subscription optins, and call-to-action buttons.</p>\n<p>Based on the Bootstrap framework with some impressive jQuery scripts, London has a lot to offer.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-london/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with London Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/templatic-home-quest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. HomeQuest</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/templatic-home-quest/ \" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/homequest.jpg\" alt=\"homequest\" width=\"775\" height=\"255\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224063\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/homequest.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/homequest-300x99.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/homequest-768x253.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re running a real estate classifieds portal, then HomeQuest is the theme you want. Your clients will love its searchable map and other advanced search features.</p>\n<p>HomeQuest was specifically designed to earn you more money. With tons of different submissions packages, an option to claim properties, and several ad space areas; you’ll be raking in the dough in no time!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/templatic-home-quest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with HomeQuest Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-oslo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Oslo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-oslo/ \" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/oslo.jpg\" alt=\"oslo\" width=\"775\" height=\"217\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224064\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/oslo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/oslo-300x84.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/oslo-768x215.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>By utilizing Bootstrap, Oslo packs quite a punch. It even has several jQuery scripts to make it even more powerful.</p>\n<p>You can use its pre-built homepage to get up and running immediately, or customize Oslo to your heart’s content with unlimited color options, header settings, and widget areas.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpcasa-oslo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Oslo Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-main-street/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Mainstreet</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-main-street/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/main-sreet.png\" alt=\"main street\" width=\"740\" height=\"491\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225347\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/main-sreet.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/main-sreet-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This theme might be called Mainstreet, but you’ll think you just downloaded Easy Street thanks to its incredibly simple set up. The drag and drop builder makes starting your real estate website a breeze, letting you earn money in no time flat.</p>\n<p>Visitors can search the MLS thanks to the dsIDXPress plugin. Plus, you can display your listings in any currency.</p>\n<p>This theme works perfectly for multiple agents as well. Each agent will be given their own dashboard.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gorillathemes-main-street/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Mainstreet Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/real-estate-lite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. Real Estate Lite</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/real-estate-lite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-lite.png\" alt=\"real-estate-lite\" width=\"775\" height=\"307\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224066\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-lite.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-lite-300x119.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-lite-768x304.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This free theme is one of the essential WordPress real estate themes because it’s a complete solution for your needs.</p>\n<p>This theme is translation-ready and highly customizable. You can customize the background, colors, logo area, menus, and header area. It also has multiple widget-ready areas, as well as options for 1, 2, or 3 column layouts.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/real-estate-lite/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Real Estate Lite Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/real-estate-right-now/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. Real Estate Right Now</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/real-estate-right-now/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-right-now.png\" alt=\"real-estate-right-now\" width=\"775\" height=\"343\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224067\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-right-now.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-right-now-300x133.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-right-now-768x340.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Real Estate Right Now is perfect if you’re selling properties in different currencies or languages. Plus, you can change your theme’s color scheme from dark to light with a single click of your mouse.</p>\n<p>You can choose from a full or boxed layout, and you’re given 3 footer widgets. For a free theme, it’s a great option!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/real-estate-right-now/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Real Estate Right Now Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/new-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. New Estate</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/new-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/new-estate.png\" alt=\"new-estate\" width=\"775\" height=\"260\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224068\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/new-estate.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/new-estate-300x101.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/new-estate-768x258.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>New Estate can be downloaded for free for a full set of basic features, or you can upgrade to the premium version for even more options.</p>\n<p>The free version has everything you need for running a multi-agent website. You can even allow clients to upload their own properties.</p>\n<p>The premium version comes with a beautiful image slider, maps, and dedicated support.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/new-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with New Estate Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/di-business/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Di Business</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\" https://wordpress.org/themes/di-business/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/di.png\" alt=\"di business\" width=\"740\" height=\"484\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225346\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/di.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/di-300x196.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Di Business is WooCommerce ready and includes several templates, including a 1-click demo site installer. You can be up-and-running in no time flat!</p>\n<p>This theme is clean, modern, and customizable. We loved that it’s compatible with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared (2018)\">most popular page builder plugins</a>. You can tweak your website to perfection with no coding skills needed.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/di-business/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Di Business Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-7/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Real Estate 7</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-7/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-7.jpg\" alt=\"real-estate-7\" width=\"774\" height=\"359\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224070\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-7.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-7-300x139.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/real-estate-7-768x356.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Whether you’re selling properties to buy or to rent, Real Estate 7 has got you covered!</p>\n<p>This theme includes plenty of plugins and even a 1-click demo installer to get your site ready quickly. The theme even guarantees top-notch support and free updates.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-7/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Real Estate 7 Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-myhome-real-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. MyHome</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\" https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-myhome-real-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/MyHome.png\" alt=\"MyHome\" width=\"600\" height=\"257\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224071\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/MyHome.png 600w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/MyHome-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re looking to try a premium theme, but are feeling unsure, then you’ll appreciate MyHome’s 14-day free trial option.</p>\n<p>MyHome includes 6 1-click website demos, and 14 homepage templates. They boast that their included drag and drop page builder has even more modules than WPBakery! This theme can also be adapted for any currency or language.</p>\n<p>The advanced search functions include keyword autocomplete, map searches, and classic searches. Clients can also save their searches, if desired.</p>\n<p>This theme also includes plenty of options for images and videos, including a feature that allows you to do virtual property tours.</p>\n<p>Monetization is also a breeze thanks to WooCommerce integration and payment gateways for PayPal, Stripe, and direct bank transfers.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-myhome-real-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with MyHome Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-houzez/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Houzez</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-houzez/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/houzez.jpg\" alt=\"houzez\" width=\"600\" height=\"233\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224072\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/houzez.jpg 600w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/houzez-300x117.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Houzez is GDPR compliant right off the bat, and works well with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/visual-composer/\" title=\"WPBakery Page Builder Review (Formerly Visual Composer)\">WPBakery</a>, the most popular drag and drop plugin, to make building your website simple as pie.</p>\n<p>This theme has also been fully translated into 20 different languages, and can be translated into more via <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-translation-plugins-compared/\" title=\"11 Best WordPress Translation Plugins Compared (2018)\">plugins</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-houzez/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Houzez Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-wp-residence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. WP Residence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\" https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-wp-residence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WP-Residence.jpg\" alt=\"WP Residence\" width=\"600\" height=\"305\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224073\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WP-Residence.jpg 600w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WP-Residence-300x153.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This theme allows you to give your clients the ability to upload their own properties. You can let users upload their properties for free, or set up a fee for submissions.</p>\n<p>With over 400 theme options, WP Residence is highly customizable so you can make your website perfectly match your brand. Or, if you’re in a hurry, you can use 1 of their 12 pre-built demo sites and simply add in your own content.</p>\n<p>WP Residence has been translated into 32 different languages as well.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-wp-residence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with WP Residence Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-real-homes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Real Homes</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-real-homes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Real-Homes.png\" alt=\"Real Homes\" width=\"700\" height=\"330\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224074\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Real-Homes.png 700w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Real-Homes-300x141.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Real Homes has an advanced, customizable, properties search function that you and your clients will both appreciate. It also has a map search function that works with Google Maps’ API. We especially liked the compare tool that allowed potential clients to look at properties side-by-side.</p>\n<p>This theme has the option of using grid or list layouts to showcase your real estate listings. Plus, there are numerous image gallery templates!</p>\n<p>Real Homes includes its own child theme for easy customization with snippets, as well as a few premium plugins such as Slider Revolution and WPBakery.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeforest-real-homes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Real Homes Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best WordPress real estate themes of 2018!</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this post, you might also like our comparison of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-event-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Events Plugins Compared (2018)\">best WordPress events plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-themes/\">21 Best WordPress Real Estate Themes for 2018 (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"Pretty Links Review – Manage Affiliate Links with Ease\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/pretty-links/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/pretty-links/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 05 Dec 2018 13:58:50 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=225496\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:612:\"<p>Looking for a plugin to manage your affiliate links, redirects, and social links in WordPress? The Pretty Links plugin does exactly that (plus a whole lot more!) to help you manage your links. With this plugin, you can shorten, cloak, track, and share your WordPress links easily. In this Pretty Links review, we’ll take a [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/pretty-links/\">Pretty Links Review – Manage Affiliate Links with Ease</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18511:\"<p>Looking for a plugin to manage your affiliate links, redirects, and social links in WordPress? The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pretty Links</a> plugin does exactly that (plus a whole lot more!) to help you manage your links. With this plugin, you can shorten, cloak, track, and share your WordPress links easily. </p>\n<p>In this Pretty Links review, we’ll take a look at its features, functionalities, pricing, and more. </p>\n<h3>About Pretty Links</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-site.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"419\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225515\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-site.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-site-300x162.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-site-768x415.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pretty Links</a> is a powerful all-in-one WordPress links management plugin. It lets you create clean, simple URLs on your WordPress site from which you can redirect to any other URL. You can create redirects for your existing site content or for external links like affiliate links, group them, and easily share them on multiple platforms using this plugin. </p>\n<p>It allows you to turn your long, ugly affiliate links into pretty links. If you’re a blogger or an affiliate marketer, this plugin has a bunch of features to enable you to add and organize affiliate links in WordPress. </p>\n<p>It’s also a link shortener tool that allows you to shorten your posts and pages URLs which you can share on social media platforms and in your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\">email campaigns</a>. Unlike other URL-shrinking services like TinyURL, budurl, and bit.ly, this plugin allows you to create shortlinks originating from your own domain.  </p>\n<p>Pretty Links is more than a link management tool; it also has a link tracking feature. It tracks each hit on your pretty URL and provides a full report on the traffic source, browser, operating system, host, etc. </p>\n<h3>Pretty Links Review: Getting Started with Pretty Links</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pretty Links</a> is a simple and easy-to-use WordPress plugin with a clean interface. </p>\n<p>To get started, you’ll need to install the plugin on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a>. If you need a step-by-step guide, here’s our tutorial on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>. </p>\n<p>After the plugin is installed on your site, you’ll need to activate the plugin license. Visit <strong>Pretty Link &raquo; Activate Pro</strong> from your WordPress dashboard and enter your plugin license. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/activate-pretty-links.jpg\" alt=\"activate-pretty-links\" width=\"775\" height=\"404\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225517\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/activate-pretty-links.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/activate-pretty-links-300x156.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/activate-pretty-links-768x400.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now that you’ve activated your plugin license, you can go ahead and review the plugin&#8217;s settings by visiting <strong>Pretty Link &raquo; Options</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-options.jpg\" alt=\"pretty-links-options\" width=\"775\" height=\"404\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225518\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-options.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-options-300x156.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-options-768x400.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The first option, <strong>General</strong>, allows you to add a substitute URL for your site. If you have another domain that points to your WordPress install, you can activate this option by putting a check there. </p>\n<p>After each option item, there’s a <strong>quick info</strong> sign where you can click to learn more about what the option allows you to do. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-options-quick-info.jpg\" alt=\"pretty-links-options-quick-info\" width=\"775\" height=\"319\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225519\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-options-quick-info.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-options-quick-info-300x123.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-options-quick-info-768x316.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The second option, <strong>Links</strong>, allows you to configure your default link options. </p>\n<p>You can choose a default redirection type, enable tracking, enable nofollow, specify slug character count, enable Google Analytics, and more from this option. To <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-google-analytics-wordpress-site/\">enable Google Analytics</a>, you’ll need to have either <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/monsterinsights/\">MonsterInsights</a> or Google Analyticator installed on your site. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-default-link-options.jpg\" alt=\"pretty-links-default-link-options\" width=\"775\" height=\"689\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225520\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-default-link-options.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-default-link-options-300x267.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-default-link-options-768x683.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, you can review all the plugin options. </p>\n<h3>Creating Your First Pretty Link</h3>\n<p>To create your first pretty link, go to <strong>Pretty Link &raquo; Add New Link</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-pretty-link.jpg\" alt=\"add-pretty-link\" width=\"775\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225521\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-pretty-link.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-pretty-link-300x223.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-pretty-link-768x570.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>First, you can choose a redirection type. It supports various redirection types including 301 permanent, 302 temporary, 307 temporary, pretty bar, etc. As an example, we’ve selected a 307 temporary redirection in the screenshot above as we’re going to add a pretty link for an affiliate link. </p>\n<p>Next, you’ll need to enter your target URL. You can add an internal link on your site or an external affiliate link there. For example, we’ve added Avada WordPress theme’s affiliate URL in the above screenshot. </p>\n<p>Then, you’ll see a <strong>Pretty Link</strong> slug automatically generated by the plugin. The auto-generated slug is a random combination of letters so you can edit and give a memorable/ easy to read name. In the above example, we’ve used the theme’s name, </strong>avada</strong>, as the pretty link slug. </p>\n<p>Next, you can add a title for your pretty link. In this example, we added theme’s name, <strong>Avada</strong>, as the title. </p>\n<p>You can also add notes to your link. </p>\n<p>Then, click the <strong>Advanced Options</strong> link to configure advanced link options. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-advanced-options.jpg\" alt=\"pretty-links-advanced-options\" width=\"774\" height=\"334\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225522\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-advanced-options.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-advanced-options-300x129.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-advanced-options-768x331.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>First, you can add your link to a group. Pretty Links allows you to organize your links by adding them to groups. If you have pre-made groups, you can simply select one from the options or simply create a new one by clicking the <strong>Add a New Group</strong> button. </p>\n<p>In this example, we’ve selected the pre-made group <strong>Affiliate Links</strong>. To create and configure groups ahead of links, you can go to <strong>Pretty Link &raquo; Groups</strong>. </p>\n<p>Next, you can review the <strong>No Follow</strong> option. It’s checked by default because we’d set it from the default link options. </p>\n<p>Then, you can select parameter forwarding and tracking options. </p>\n<p>Below the Advanced Options, you can see <strong>Pro Options</strong>. This option includes link automation features. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-pro-options.jpg\" alt=\"pretty-links-pro-options\" width=\"774\" height=\"477\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225523\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-pro-options.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-pro-options-300x185.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-pro-options-768x473.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>You can set the expire link option but you’ll need to be extra careful to set an expired redirect link after the links expire. You can add a list of keywords to that you’d like to replace with this link in your posts and pages.</p>\n<p>In this example, we’ve added 2 keywords related to the theme. The number of keyword replacements can be defined from the plugin options. </p>\n<p>After you configure all the link options, click the <strong>Create</strong> button to save your link. </p>\n<h3>Adding Pretty Link to Your WordPress Posts</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pretty Links</a> allows you to add your pretty links directly into your posts. You can either create a new pretty link in a post or use an existing pretty link. </p>\n<p>To add a pretty link in your post, open your post editor in the visual mode. There, you’ll see an <strong>Insert Pretty Link</strong> icon in the toolbar.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/insert-pretty-link-icon.jpg\" alt=\"insert-pretty-link-icon\" width=\"774\" height=\"231\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225524\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/insert-pretty-link-icon.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/insert-pretty-link-icon-300x90.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/insert-pretty-link-icon-768x229.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>Upon clicking on the icon, you’ll see options to add a new pretty link. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-new-pretty-link-to-a-post.jpg\" alt=\"add-new-pretty-link-to-a-post\" width=\"774\" height=\"454\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225526\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-new-pretty-link-to-a-post.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-new-pretty-link-to-a-post-300x176.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/add-new-pretty-link-to-a-post-768x450.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to use an existing pretty link, you can click the <strong>Use Existing Pretty Link</strong> option. </p>\n<p>It’s easy to add pretty links to your WordPress posts and pages. </p>\n<p>After you add plenty of pretty links, write content, and publish your post, you may want to create a shortlink for the post which you can share on social media and other platforms. Pretty Links makes it easy. </p>\n<p>In the post editor page, next to your Permalink <strong>edit</strong> button, you&#8217;ll see a new button: <strong>Get Shortlink</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/get-shortlink-pretty-links.jpg\" alt=\"get-shortlink-pretty-links\" width=\"774\" height=\"229\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225525\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/get-shortlink-pretty-links.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/get-shortlink-pretty-links-300x89.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/get-shortlink-pretty-links-768x227.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>Simply click the link and you’ll get a shortlink for your post. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/copy-shortlink.jpg\" alt=\"copy-shortlink\" width=\"774\" height=\"229\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225527\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/copy-shortlink.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/copy-shortlink-300x89.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/copy-shortlink-768x227.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, you can copy the link and share it on your social platforms or send to your email subscribers. </p>\n<h3>Viewing and Sharing Your Pretty Links</h3>\n<p>To view the pretty links you created, you can go to <strong>Pretty Links &raquo; Pretty Links</strong> from your dashboard. There, you’ll see your list of pretty links. </p>\n<p>If you mouseover any link, you’ll see different options including Twitter share icon, email icon, link click stats, link edit, and more. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-list.jpg\" alt=\"pretty-links-list\" width=\"774\" height=\"376\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225528\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-list.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-list-300x146.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-list-768x373.jpg 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-list-330x160.jpg 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to share a pretty link leading to a post, you can click the Twitter icon below it and share. Similarly, you can also share the pretty link in emails. </p>\n<h3>Pretty Links: Pricing and Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pretty Links</a> is a free premium WordPress plugin. You can download its free version <strong>Pretty Links Lite</strong> from official WordPress plugin repository and use it on as many sites as you want. </p>\n<p>For advanced features and options, you’ll need to buy its premium plans. There’re 3 pricing plans: <strong>Beginner</strong>, <strong>Marketer</strong>, and <strong>Super Affiliate</strong>. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-pricing.jpg\" alt=\"pretty-links-pricing\" width=\"774\" height=\"568\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225529\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-pricing.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-pricing-300x220.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pretty-links-pricing-768x564.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The <strong>Beginner</strong> plan normally costs $118 per year. It allows you to use Pretty Links on 1 website. Its features include advanced redirect types, auto create pretty links, and auto-link keywords.</p>\n<p>The <strong>Marketer</strong> plan normally costs $198 per year. This plan allows you to use the plugin on up to 5 websites. It includes all the features included in the Beginner plan and adds advanced addons. </p>\n<p>The <strong>Super Affiliate</strong> plan’s normal price is $398 per year. With this plan, you’ll get the plugin license for up to 25 websites. It includes all the features provided in Beginner and Marketer and additionally offers priority support. </p>\n<p>With all the plans, you’ll get 1 year of support and updates. The great thing about Pretty Links is that you can get a 100% risk-free money back guarantee for 14 days if you aren’t satisfied with the plugin. </p>\n<p>The plugin has a full set of articles in the <strong>User Manual</strong> to help you configure and use the plugin. For premium support, you’ll need to send a support request by logging into the Pretty Links website. </p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using Pretty Links on Your WordPress Site</h3>\n<p>The Pretty Links plugin is a powerful plugin for link management, automation, affiliate management, and shortlinks. It has a complete set of features to allow you to add affiliate links, organize, and manage other links. You can easily shorten your links and make them pretty links. </p>\n<p>Using Pretty Links is fairly easy. Anyone who&#8217;s familiar with the WordPress interface can use this plugin. You don’t need any coding skills to use this plugin to manage your links like a pro.</p>\n<p>We believe that <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pretty-links-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pretty Links</a> is an all-in-one link management plugin perfect for affiliate marketers, bloggers, social media marketers, and anyone else who wants to make WordPress links attractive and memorable. </p>\n<p>We give it 5 out of 5 stars. Here’s the breakdown of our review score: </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/pretty-links/\">Pretty Links Review – Manage Affiliate Links with Ease</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/pretty-links/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:28:\"https://www.isitwp.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:18:{s:6:\"server\";s:17:\"Sucuri/Cloudproxy\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Tue, 18 Dec 2018 14:24:33 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:11:\"x-sucuri-id\";s:5:\"12003\";s:16:\"x-xss-protection\";s:13:\"1; mode=block\";s:15:\"x-frame-options\";s:10:\"SAMEORIGIN\";s:22:\"x-content-type-options\";s:7:\"nosniff\";s:25:\"strict-transport-security\";a:2:{i:0;s:44:\"max-age=31536000; includeSubdomains; preload\";i:1;s:13:\"max-age=86400\";}s:23:\"content-security-policy\";s:26:\"upgrade-insecure-requests;\";s:10:\"set-cookie\";s:98:\"srv_id=587cf80a2a75f4f026cdf9547549c7f8; expires=Tue, 18-Dec-18 14:33:19 GMT; max-age=3600; path=/\";s:4:\"vary\";s:6:\"Cookie\";s:7:\"expires\";s:29:\"Thu, 19 Nov 1981 08:52:00 GMT\";s:13:\"cache-control\";s:35:\"no-store, no-cache, must-revalidate\";s:6:\"pragma\";s:8:\"no-cache\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"edfc6a85afd878e05cea2102641daab2\"\";s:12:\"x-robots-tag\";s:15:\"noindex, follow\";s:9:\"x-backend\";s:22:\"awesomemotive-web1.com\";s:14:\"x-sucuri-cache\";s:3:\"HIT\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20130911070210\";}", "no");
